EPerhaps%20never%20before%20has%20Britain's%20South%20Asian%20diaspora%20enjoyed%20such%20prominence%20on%20the%20country's%20biggest%20political%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20ruling%20Conservative%20Party's%20annual%20conference%20in%20Manchester%20this%20week%2C%20two%20of%20the%20UK's%20highest-ranking%20officials%20highlighted%20their%20Indian%20heritage%20in%20efforts%20to%20rally%20the%20party%20faithful.%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20declared%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20stand%20before%20you%20today%20as%20the%20first%20non-white%20leader%20in%20our%20country's%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20home%20secretary%2C%20Suella%20Braverman%2C%20acknowledged%20the%20%26quot%3Bwind%20of%20change%20that%20carried%20my%20own%20parents%20across%20the%20globe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20Ms%20Braverman%20contrasted%20the%2020th%20century's%20demographic%20currents%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bhurricane%26quot%3B%20of%20migration%20now%20bearing%20down%20on%20Europe%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20used%20his%20family's%20migration%20from%20India%20via%20East%20Africa%20to%20highlight%20his%20debt%20to%20British%20traditions.%20The%20message%20was%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20effort%20by%20the%20premier%20to%20reintroduce%20himself%20to%20the%20country%20as%20he%20prepares%20to%20face%20the%20voters%20for%20the%20first%20time%20as%20the%20their%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20grandparents%20did%20not%20emigrate%20to%20just%20Leicester%20or%20Southampton%2C%20but%20to%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sunak%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BThey%20came%20here%20because%20our%20country%20stands%20for%20a%20set%20of%20values.%20We%20are%20the%20home%20of%20fair%20play%2C%20the%20best%20of%20British.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20comment%20highlighted%20how%20little%20emphasis%20has%20been%20placed%20on%20Mr%20Sunak's%20minority%20status%20since%20he%20became%20prime%20minister%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20back-to-back%20resignations%20of%20Boris%20Johnson%20and%20Liz%20Truss%20last%20year.%20True%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20hasn't%20hid%20his%20heritage%2C%20speaking%20in%20interviews%20about%20being%20a%20practicing%20Hindu%20while%20wearing%20a%20red%20kalava%20string%20around%20his%20wrist%20to%20mark%20his%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20other%20leaders%20of%20South%20Asia%20decent%2C%20such%20as%20London%20Mayor%20Sadiq%20Khan%20and%20First%20Minister%20of%20the%20devolved%20Scottish%20government%20Humza%20Yousaf%20have%20both%20spoken%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20their%20roots%2C%20with%20the%20former%20speaking%20about%20the%20racism%20he%20faced%20growing%20up%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20rising%20hate%20crimes%20in%20the%20country.%20Still%2C%20Mr%20Sunak's%20rise%20to%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20power%20in%20a%20government%20that%20until%201947%20ruled%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20as%20a%20colony%20has%20gone%20with%20little%20of%20the%20fanfare%20that%20accompanied%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Barack%20Obama's%20election%20as%20America's%20first%20black%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20fact%20acknowledged%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20expressing%20pride%20that%20being%20Britain's%20first%20Asian%20prime%20minister%20%26quot%3Bis%20just%20not%20a%20big%20deal.%26quot%3B%20Still%2C%20the%20comments%20showed%20Mr%20Sunak's%20heritage%20may%20be%20of%20increasing%20relevance%20ahead%20of%20a%20general%20election%20that%20must%20be%20held%20by%20January%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20personal%20level%2C%20the%20migration%20of%20Mr%20Sunak's%20forebearers%20from%20the%20Punjab%20region%20of%20what%20is%20now%20Pakistan%20and%20eventually%20to%20Britain%20helps%20fill%20out%20the%20backstory%20of%20a%20prime%20minister%20who%20has%20so%20far%20enjoyed%20little%20public%20enthusiasm.%20That%20was%20underscored%20by%20Mr%20Sunak's%20decision%20to%20have%20his%20wife%2C%20Akshata%20Murty%2C%20introduce%20him%20at%20the%20conference%2C%20a%20break%20with%20tradition%20seen%20as%20an%20import%20of%20American-style%20First%20Lady%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Sunak%2C%20a%20former%20Goldman%20Sachs%20Group%20banker%2C%20met%20Ms%20Murty%20while%20attending%20Stanford%20University.%20She's%20the%20daughter%20Indian%20billionaire%20Narayana%20Murthy%2C%20a%20co-founder%20of%20Infosys%20Ltd.%2C%20and%20her%20personal%20fortune%20contributes%20greatly%20to%20Mr%20Sunak's%20status%20as%20British%20richest-ever%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAspiration%20runs%20through%20his%20DNA%20like%20it%20does%20this%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Murty%20said%20of%20her%20husband.%20%26quot%3BAspiration%20is%20what%20drove%20his%20family%20many%20years%20ago%20to%20move%20to%20the%20UK.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20broadly%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20must%20balance%20Britain's%20support%20for%20the%20ideals%20of%20multiculturism%20with%20anxiety%20over%20a%20record%20surge%20in%20migration%2C%20particularly%20asylum-seekers%20crossing%20the%20English%20Channel%20in%20small%20boats.%20Ms%20Braverman%2C%20who%20oversees%20migration%20as%20home%20secretary%2C%20told%20Conservatives%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20immigration%20was%20%26quot%3Balready%20too%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20days%20after%20decrying%20the%20%26quot%3Bmisguided%20dogma%20of%20multiculturalism%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20speech%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Sunak%2C%20I%20think%2C%20is%20using%20his%20own%20story%2C%20authentically%20in%20his%20account%20of%20it%2C%20to%20put%20the%20Conservatives%20back%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20debate%2C%20so%20this%20isn't%20an%20existential%20debate%20about%20the%20failure%20of%20British%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sunder%20Katwala%2C%20director%20of%20the%20British%20Future%20think%20tank%20which%20explores%20attitudes%20toward%20identity%20and%20integration.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20back%20to%20a%20debate%20about%20can%20you%20get%20a%20grip%20on%20the%20immigration%20system%20and%20how%20to%20manage%20immigration%20well.%26