20Sunak's%20latest%20rhetoric%20might%20be%20a%20pitch%20to%20win%20over%20support%20from%20a%20growing%20segment%20of%20the%20British%20population%20with%20South%20Asian%20heritage%2C%20many%20of%20whom%2C%20like%20Mr%20Sunak%2C%20supported%20Brexit.%20Recent%20census%20data-which%20show%20that%20people%20from%20Asian%20ethnic%20groups%20make%20up%20more%20than%209%25%20of%20the%20UK%20population-points%20to%20increasing%20immigration%20from%20India%2C%20where%20support%20for%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20makes%20him%20more%20human%20and%20softens%20his%20wealthy%20persona%2C%20according%20to%20Sunder%20Katwala.%20%26quot%3BIt%20becomes%20a%20relatable%20story%20because%20it's%20about%20more%20universal%20themes%20of%20family%20and%20opportunity%20and%20aspiration%20and%20community%20rather%20than%20being%20about%20where%20he's%20ended%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20the%20Conservatives%20have%20also%20made%20a%20concerted%20effort%20since%20coming%20into%20power%20in%202010%20to%20cement%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20India%20and%20the%20Hindu%20population.%20That%20includes%20hosting%20a%20huge%20concert%20in%202015%20at%20the%20iconic%20Wembley%20stadium%20to%20welcome%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20blocking%20efforts%20to%20make%20caste%20discrimination%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Sunak%20and%20PM%20Modi's%20governments%20are%20currently%20negotiating%20a%20trade%20deal%2C%20which%20could%20further%20deepen%20links%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20The%20Indian%20side%20is%20seeking%20provisions%20to%20allow%20its%20workers%20freer%20movement%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20UK%2C%20although%20Mr%20Sunak%20says%20a%20looser%20visa%20policy%20isn't%20being%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20Mr%20Sunak's%20embrace%20of%20his%20own%20heritage%20will%20help%20him%20navigate%20Britain's%20fraug