.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBuenos%20Aires%20takes%20this%20year's%20crown%2C%20with%20rates%20that%20are%20set%20to%20jump%20by%2017%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hotel%20Monitor%202024%20report%20from%20American%20Express%20Global%20Business%20Travel%20released%20Thursday.%20It%20examines%20how%20hotel%20prices%20are%20fluctuating%20in%20more%20than%2080%20cities%20around%20the%20world%2C%20with%20forecasts%20based%20on%20criteria%20such%20as%20currently%20listed%20prices%2C%20broader%20macroeconomic%20trends%2C%20hotel%20pipelines%20and%20historic%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cem%3EHere%20are%20the%20top%2010%20cities%20around%20the%20world%20where%20hotel%20prices%20are%20set%20to%20soar%20most%20dramatically-along%20with%20how%20much%20more%20you%20can%20expect%20to%20pay%20in%20local%20currency%2C%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EJakarta%2C%20Indonesia%3A%2010.9%25%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EBoston%2C%20US%3A%2011.3%25%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EParis%2C%20France%3A%2011%25%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EDelhi%2C%20India%3A%2012%25%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EChicago%2C%20US%3A%2012.6%25%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EBogota%2C%20Colombia%3A%2014.1%25%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EChennai%2C%20India%3A%2014.6%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECairo%2C%20Egypt%3A%2014.6%25%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EMumbai%2C%20India%3A%2015%25%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EBuenos%20Aires%2C%20Argentina%3A%2017.5%25%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Cp%3EHotel%20prices%20reflect%20much%20more%20than%20a%20destination's%20current%20popularity%20with%20travelers.%20In%20the%20Argentina%20capital%2C%20rates%20are%20largely%20being%20driven%20by%20the%20country's%20ongoing%20hyperinflation%20crisis%2C%20which%20in%20September%20reached%20its%20worst%20levels%20since%201991.%20(Notably%2C%20the%20Amex%20study%20calculates%20rate%20hikes%20in%20the%20local%20currency.)%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20rising%20prices%20in%20Buenos%20Aires%20are%20still%20likely%20to%20translate%20to%20deep%20savings%20for%20most%20anyone%20visiting%20from%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecond-place%20Mumbai%20has%20a%20more%20straightforward%20narrative.%20Its%20hotels%20are%20expected%20to%20rise%20in%20cost%20by%2015%25%20year%20over%20year%3B%20that's%20undoubtedly%20a%20product%20of%20fast-growing%20domestic%20wealth%20and%20a%20long-delayed%20post-pandemic%20travel%20recovery.%20And%20given%20both%20of%20those%20factors%20apply%20countrywide%2C%20it's%20no%20surprise%20that%20India%20claims%20three%20cities%20in%20the%20report's%20top%2010%20list%3A%20Chennai%20and%20Delhi%20ranked%20fourth%20and%20seventh%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERounding%20out%20the%20top%2010%20are%20cities%20where%20tourism%20has%20been%20booming.%20Whereas%20Cairo%20has%20benefited%20from%20a%20largely%20leisure-driven%20audience%2C%20Chicago%2C%20Paris%20and%20Boston%20rank%20in%20the%20top%2010%20thanks%20to%20gains%20in%20business%20travel.%20The%20region%20with%20the%20most%20moderate%20rate%20increases%20is%20Australasia%2C%20where%20no%20single%20city%20is%20seeing%20projected%20increases%20greater%20than%206.8%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrices%20are%20expected%20to%20rise%20at%20least%20somewhat%20in%20all%2080%20cities%20examined%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDavid%20Reimer%2C%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20global%20clients%20at%20Amex%20GBT%2C%20sees%20several%20macro%20trends%20continuing%20to%20influence%20hotel%20pricing%20at%20a%20global%20level.%20Staffing%20shortages%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20problem%20in%20the%20hospitality%20industry%2C%20forcing%20some%20hotels%20to%20limit%20inventory-meaning%20they're%20leaving%20rooms%20deliberately%20unsold-as%20a%20coping%20mechanism.%20That%20spreads%20soaring%20operating%20costs%20among%20fewer%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20issue%20of%20supply-the%20number%20of%20hotel%20rooms%20in%20any%20market-not%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20there%20is%20lagging%20supply%20but%20demand%20remains%20high%2C%20rates%20will%20also%20rise%2C%26quot%3B%20Reimer%20says.%20The%20inverse%20can%20also%20be%20true.%20Rates%20are%20predicted%20to%20rise%20only%20moderately%20in%20cities%20such%20as%20Riyadh%20and%20New%20York%20City%2C%20which%20will%20add%20a%20large%20number%20of%20new%20hotel%20rooms%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%20The%20report%20predicts%20that%20prices%20in%20those%20markets%20will%20be%20up%204.6%25%20and%206.8%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(The%20report%20caveats%20that%20recent%20legislation%20curtailing%20short-term%20rentals%20in%20New%20York%20City%20may%20drive%20prices%20up%20in%20ways%20that%20are%20not%20reflected%20by%20Amex%20GBT's%20data%20models.)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoston%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20few%20new%20hotels%20in%20the%20works-which%20will%20be%20problematic%20for%20consumers%20as%20the%20city%20continues%20to%20show%20strong%20growth%20as%20a%20business%20travel%20hub%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20its%20perennial%20leisure%20and%20university-related%20travel%20demand.%20That%20explains%20the%20city's%20sharp%2011.5%25%20projected%20spike.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EParis%20Landmarks%20Amid%20French%20Economy%20Growth%20Surge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EParis%20ranks%20in%20the%20top%2010%20with%20highest%20hotel%20rate%20increases%20in%202024.%20Photographer%3A%20Nathan%20Laine%2FBloomberg%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20there's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20talk%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20continuation%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20we're%20seeing%20some%20kinds%20of%20business%20travel%20actually%20surpassing%202019%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Reimer%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20it's%20people%20traveling%20for%20trade%20shows%20or%20small%20internal%20meetings%20of%2020%20people%20or%20fewer%2C%20he%20says.%20At%20some%20companies%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20trips%20related%20to%20those%20more-intimate%20corporate%20functions%20have%20surpassed%202019%20levels%20by%20as%20much%20as%2025%25.%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20that%20that%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20our%20fastest%20growing%20segment%2C%26quot%3B%20Reimer%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20even%20with%20the%20projected%20hotel%20rate%20increases%2C%20some%20of%20these%20cities%20still%20offer%20deep%20value.%20A%20room%20at%20an%20over-the-top%20hotel%20in%20Buenos%20Aires%20during%20peak%20season%2C%20for%20example%2C%20can%20cost%20just%20%24600%20a%20night%3B%20a%2017.5%25%20increase%20would%20add%20just%20a%20little%20over%20%24100.%20Compare%20that%20to%20%242%2C000%20a%20night%20in%20Paris%20during%20high%20season-the%20current%20going%20rate%20at%20a%20palace%20hotel-and%20the%20smaller-seeming%2011%25%20increase%2C%20valued%20at%20around%20%24200%2C%20adds%20twice%20as%20much%20sting%20in%20absolute%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696564800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F0b6hc4go_hotel-generic_625x300_24_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-indian-cities-among-worlds-top-10-for-soaring-hotel-prices-what-it-means-4454844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hotel%20room%20rates%20in%20major%20cities%20from%20Boston%20to%20Mumbai%20are%20expected%20to%20jump%20by%20double%20digits%2C%20even%20after%20predictions%20that%20prices%20were%20finally%20hitting%20a%20ceiling%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-indian-cities-among-worlds-top-10-for-soaring-hotel-prices-what-it-means-4454844%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-indian-cities-among-worlds-top-10-for-soaring-hotel-prices-what-it-means-44548