's%20most%20prolific%20batter%20in%20ODIs%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20is%20reportedly%20down%20with%20high%20fever%20and%20will%20be%20tested%20for%20dengue%20on%20Friday%20before%20a%20final%20call%20is%20taken%20on%20the%20matter.%20News%20agency%20PTI%20had%20earlier%20reported%20that%20Gill%20was%20down%20with%20high%20fever%20and%20will%20be%20tested%20for%20dengue%20on%20Friday%20before%20a%20final%20call%20is%20taken%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShubhman%20has%20had%20high%20fever%20since%20landing%20in%20Chennai.%20His%20tests%20are%20being%20done.%20He%20will%20have%20tests%20on%20Friday%20and%20a%20call%20will%20be%20taken%20on%20his%20participation%20in%20opening%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BCCI%20source%20privy%20to%20team%20developments%20told%20PTI%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20not%20jump%20the%20gun.%20If%20it's%20normal%20viral%20fever%2C%20he%20could%20play%20on%20antibiotics%20but%20it's%20completely%20the%20medical%20team's%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhysical%20recovery%20of%20dengue%20patients%20vary%20and%20it%20normally%20takes%20around%207-10%20days%20to%20be%20up%20and%20match%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIshan%20Kishan%20could%20be%20in%20line%20to%20open%20in%20case%20Gill%20is%20ruled%20out.%20Gill%20is%20India's%20top-scorer%20in%20ODIs%20in%202023%2C%20having%20scored%C2%A01%2C230%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2072.35%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20just%20above%20105.%20He%20has%20scored%20five%20centuries%20and%20five%20fifties%20this%20year%2C%20with%20the%20best%20of%20208.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20kicked%20off%20on%20Thursday%2C%20with%20New%20Zealand%20thrashing%20defending%20champions%20England%20by%20nine%20wickets%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Th