%3Eaccused%20the%20Indian%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20being%20behind%20the%20assassination%20of%20a%20Canadian%20national%2C%20India%20had%20angrily%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%2C%20expelled%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20measure%20and%20asked%20for%20downsizing%20of%20the%20diplomatic%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20charged%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20outside%20a%20Canadian%20Gurudwara%20in%20June%2C%20as%20a%20pro-Khalistani%20terrorist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20followed%20by%20Associated%20Press%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-asks-canada-to-repatriate-around-40-diplomats-report%5C%22%3Ereported%20earlier%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20India%20had%20asked%20Canada%20to%20remove%2041%20diplomats%20from%20their%20Indian%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20Thursday%E2%80%99s%20briefing%2C%20Bagchi%20refused%20to%20mention%20the%20number%20of%20diplomats%20or%20the%20deadline%20for%20them%20to%20remain%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20I%20would%20not%20like%20to%20get%20into%20the%20details%20of%20diplomatic%20conversations.%20As%20we%20mentioned%2C%20I%20think%20last%20week%2C%20given%20that%20Canadian%20diplomatic%20presence%20is%20very%20much%20higher%2C%20we%20would%20assume%20that%20there%20would%20be%20a%20reduction.%20I%20think%20that%20broadly%20covers%20those%20issues%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20pointed%20out%20that%20Canada%20had%20indicated%20that%20it%20will%20impact%20consular%20services%2C%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6it%E2%80%99s%20up%20to%20the%20Canadian%20side%20who%20they%20choose%20to%20staff%20their%20High%20Commission%20with%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndians%20have%20long%20been%20going%20to%20Canada%20for%20study%20and%20work.%20Around%2040%25%20of%20international%20students%20in%20Canada%20are%20from%20India.%20Further%2C%20Indian%20tourists%20are%20the%20largest%20spenders%20among%20any%20nationality%20as%20per%20a%202021%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Canada%2C%20people%20of%20Indian%20origin%20account%20for%20about%203.7%25%20of%20the%20population%20or%201.4%20million.%20Besides%2C%20770%2C000%20people%20reported%20their%20religion%20as%20Sikhism%2C%20about%202%25%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada%2C%20along%20with%20its%20close%20allies%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20have%20repeatedly%20asked%20India%20to%20join%20the%20investigation.%20India%20has%20responded%20that%20it%20will%20be%20willing%20to%20look%20at%20any%20specific%20information%20when%20it%20is%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20United%20States%20has%20become%20important%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20American%20ambassador%20to%20Canada%20David%20Cohen%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fshared-intelligence-of-five-eye-partners-informed-trudeaus-allegations-says-us-envoy-to-canada%5C%22%3Eintelligence%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Five%20eyes%E2%80%99%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20led%20to%20Trudeau%20going%20public%20with%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%20that%20while%20Canadian%20intelligence%20had%20found%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-canada-hardeep-singh-nijjar-intelligence-spy-agency%5C%22%3Esmoking%20gun%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20US%20had%20also%20provided%20inputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnewsletters%2Fnational-security-daily%2F2023%2F10%2F03%2Fwhy-bidens-mum-on-the-india-canada-spat-00119709%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPolitico%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20US%20ambassador%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20had%20told%20his%20colleagues%20in%20the%20embassy%20that%20%E2%80%9Crelations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20U.S.%20could%20get%20worse%20for%2