bail%20the%20exception.%20Cases%20continue%20literally%20for%20decades.%20Two%20managed%20to%20secure%20freedom%20from%20UAPA%2C%20one%20with%20an%20acquittal%20and%20the%20other%2C%20a%20discharge.%20Over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20patriotism%2C%20national%20security%20and%20alleged%20anti-national%20activities%20have%20been%20included%20in%20the%20array%20of%20charges%20in%20the%20UAPA%20arsenal%2C%20as%20the%20latest%20instance%20of%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20editor%20of%20news%20portal%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20against%20Purkayastha%20and%20the%20head%20of%20its%20human%20resources%20department%2C%20Amit%20Chakravarty%2C%20cites%20Sections%2013%20(unlawful%20activities)%2C%2016%20(terrorist%20act)%2C%2017%20(raising%20funds%20for%20terrorist%20acts)%2C%2018%20(conspiracy)%20and%2022%20(C)%20(offences%20by%20companies%2C%20trusts)%20in%20the%20UAPA%2C%20along%20with%20IPC%20sections%20153A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20group)%20and%20120B%20(criminal%20conspiracy).%20Sec%20153%20A%20against%20the%20media%20is%20another%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Farrest%2520warrant%2520against%2520paranjoy%2520guha%2520thakurta%3A%2520Punitive%2520and%2520Intimidatory%2520%25E2%2580%2593%2520Free%2520Speech%2520Collective(opens%2520in%2520a%2520new%2520tab)%2520freespeechcollective.in%2F2021%2F01%2F21%2Farrest-warrant-against-paranjoy-guha-thakurta-punitive-and-intimidatory%2F%5C%22%3E%C2%A0favourite%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20law%20enforcing%20agencies%20and%20has%20been%20used%20against%20a%20number%20of%20journalists%2C%20including%20Neha%20Dixit%20and%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20UAPA%20has%20been%20indiscriminatingly%20used%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20to%20charge%20human%20rights%20activists%2C%20lawyers%2C%20students%2C%20workers%20and%20tribals%2C%20other%20draconian%20acts%20like%20The%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20The%20