erance%20band%20for%20the%20month%20of%20October.%20This%2C%20after%20India%E2%80%99s%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20(CPI)%2C%20a%20key%20measure%20of%20retail%20inflation%2C%20reached%20a%20staggering%207.44%25%20in%20July%2C%20marking%20a%2015-month%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20surge%20in%20prices%20exceeded%20the%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20inflation%20tolerance%20band%20of%202-6%25%20for%20the%20seventh%20time%20and%20went%20beyond%207%25%20thrice%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F15072862%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F15072862%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F15072862%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI%20is%20calculated%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20weighted%20average%20of%20around%20450%20items%20of%20which%20almost%2050%25%20are%20food%20related.%20The%20recent%20rise%20in%20the%20CPI%2C%20driven%20in%20large%20part%20by%20soaring%20food%20prices%2C%20is%20leaving%20households%20grappling%20with%20the%20impact%20on%20their%20daily%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETomatoes%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20saw%20a%20dramatic%20price%20hike%20between%20July%20and%20August%2C%20with%20costs%20doubling%20in%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks.%20For%20the%20first%20three%20weeks%20of%20June%2C%20tomatoes%20cost%20around%20Rs%2020%2Fkilo.%20In%20the%20third%20week%20of%20that%20month%2C%20tomato%20prices%20doubled%20to%20Rs%2040%2Fkilo%2C%20and%20then%20shot%20up%20to%20Rs%20100%2Fkilo%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%20In%20August%2C%20prices%20reached%20R