20a%20vegetarian%20thali%20rose%20by%2024%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Rs%2033.8%20and%20that%20of%20a%20non-vegetarian%20thali%20by%2013%25%20to%20Rs%2067.3%20in%20August%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20released%20by%20Crisil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20surge%20was%20on%20a%20month-on-month%20basis%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Ftomato-prices-monthly-cost-of-vegetarian-thali-rises-by-34-crisil%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20vegetarian%20and%20non-vegetarian%20thalis%20rising%2034%25%20and%2013%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20compared%20to%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fview.genial.ly%2F65104f7bb85e110011315b03%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Wire%20Illustration%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20inflationary%20pressure%20from%20rising%20food%20prices%2C%20an%20uptick%20in%20the%20price%20of%20fuel%20and%20a%20depreciating%20rupee%20has%20resulted%20in%20people%20relying%20on%20their%20savings%20to%20meet%20their%20consumption%20needs.%20The%20net%20household%20savings%20of%20Indians%20dropped%20to%20a%20five-decade%20low%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F15233285%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F15233285%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F15233285%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20net%20financial%20savings%20of%20households%20fell%20to%205.1%25%20of%20the%20GDP%20in%20FY23%2C%20down%20from%207.2%25%20in%20FY22.%20The%20data%20indicates%20a%20significant%20income%20crunch%20and%20the%20temporary%20nature%20of%20the%20post-pandemic%20increase%20in%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorryingly%2C%20annual%20financial%20liabilities%20of%20households%20rose%20sharply%2C%20indicating%20larger-than-usual%20resort%20to%20loans%20for%20consumption%20purposes%2C%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fpolicy%2Feconomy-household-debt-soars-in-fy22-2898344%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F15161497%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F15161497%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F15161497%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20increased%20reliance%20on%20loans%20to%20meet%20consumption%20needs%20and%20stagnant%20income%20levels%2C%20households%E2%80%99%20loan%20repayment%20ability%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20affected%20and%20increase%20lenders%E2%80%99%20default%20risk.%20It%20is%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20top%2010%25%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20holds%2077%25%20of%20the%20total%20national%20wealth.%20Owing%20to%20the%20vast%20income%20inequality%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20result%20of%20such%20inflationary%20pressure%20on%20different%20households%20will%20be%20vastly%20different%20across%20different%20income%20bands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20survey%20that%20would%20enable%20us%20to%20adequately%20gauge%20how%20much%20money%20people%20spent%20on%20their%20consumption%20needs%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Consumer%20Expenditure%20Survey%20(CES)%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20government%20but%20its%20findings%20have%20been%20withheld.%20The%20results%20for%202022-23%20and%202023-24%20CES%20are%20likely%20to%20come%20only%20after%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fresults-of-consumer-expenditure-surveys-2022-23-2023-24-only-after-2024-elections-report%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20findings%20of%20a%20similar%20exercise%20done%20by%20the%20government%20in%202017-2018%20were%20also%20withheld%20but%20the%20leaked%20data%20had%20shown%20a%20rise%20in%20poverty%20levels%20and%20a%2045-year%20high%20in%20unemployment%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CES%20findings%20are%20also%20integral%20for%20calculating%20CPI%20and%20understanding%20the%20true%20extent%20of%20inflation%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20latest%20numbers%2C%20the%20CPI%20is%20currently%20calculated%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20more%20than%20a%20decade-old%20data%20from%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696555811000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04122115%2FIMG_2684.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Finflation-is-at-an-all-time-high-heres-what-that-looks-like%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Household%20savings%20of%20Indians%20are%20at%20a%20five-decade%20low%20amid%20soaring%20food%20prices%2C%20a%20depreciating%20rupee%20and%20uptick%20in%20fuel%20prices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Finflation-is-at-an-all-time-high-heres-what-that-looks-like%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20how%20the%20Indian%20banks%20are%20making%20%2464%20billion%20from%20a%20freebie%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe