y%20similar%20features.%20Most%20began%20early%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20most%20were%20accompanied%20by%20damning%20%E2%80%98leaks%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20mainstream%20media%2C%20and%20all%20targeted%20critics%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crackdown%20has%20focused%20on%20prominent%20human%20rights%20activists%20whose%20work%20is%20close%20to%20the%20ground%20in%20ignored%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20journalists%2C%20writers%2C%20two%20parliamentarians%2C%20a%20state%20minister%20and%20leaders%20from%20parties%20opposed%20to%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20and%20a%20comedian.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20at%20least%20two%20cases%2C%20those%20being%20raided%20were%20%E2%80%93%20and%20some%20continue%20to%20be%20%E2%80%93%20unsure%20of%20the%20charges%20against%20them%2C%20of%20which%20case%20they%20were%20being%20%E2%80%98raided%E2%80%99%20for%2C%20and%20whether%20they%20were%20being%20questioned%20as%20accused%20or%20suspect%20or%20witness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsk%20old%20timers%20when%20was%20the%20last%20time%20they%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20such%20a%20visible%20pan-India%20mobilisation%20of%20Union%20government-controlled%20agencies%20against%20individuals%20the%20ruling%20party%20does%20not%20like%20in%20such%20a%20short%20period%20of%20time%20and%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98the%20Emergency%E2%80%99.%20A%20charge%20underscored%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20one%20of%20the%20people%20jailed%20this%20week%20is%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20editor%20Prabir%20Purkayastha.%20The%20last%20time%20he%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20police%20and%20locked%20up%20was%20in%201975.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20quick%20chronology%20of%20this%20week%E2%80%99s%20raids.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%202%3A%20NIA%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%202%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnia-raids-62-andhra-pradesh-telangana-maoist%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%99s%20Sukanya%20Shantha%20has%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20officials%20of%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20arrived%20in%20groups%20of%20four%20and%20five%20at%2062%20locations%20across%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20They%20conducted%20coordinated%20raids%20on%20houses%20and%20premises%20associated%20with%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20Association%20of%20People%E2%80%99s%20Lawyers%2C%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Forum%2C%20the%20Civil%20Liberties%20Committee%2C%20the%20Committee%20for%20the%20Release%20of%20Political%20Prisoners%2C%20and%20the%20Revolutionary%20Writers%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20was%20in%20connection%20with%20what%20is%20popularly%20known%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdistricts.ecourts.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FCrl%2520MP%2520No%2520208%2520of%25202021.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Munchingiputtu%20case%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20deals%20with%20the%20alleged%20movement%20of%20Maoists%20and%20the%20transportation%20of%20Maoist%20literature%20in%20a%20village%20of%20the%20Alluri%20Sitharama%20Raju%20district.%20One%20person%20arrested%20in%202020%20had%20allegedly%20disclosed%20the%20names%20of%20some%2060%20Maoist%20activists%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20collected%2060%20books%20from%20one%20functionary%20of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Forum%2C%20alone.%20Anything%20in%20a%20vernacular%20language%2C%20which%20officials%20could%20not%20read%2C%20was%20taken%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt.%20Another%20person%20raided%20is%20counsel%20for%20many%20of%20those%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20who%20was%20asked%20to%20appear%20as%20a%20witness%20in%20the%20same%20case%2C%20in%20a%20serious%20breach%20of%20ethics%20and%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20has%20had%20a%20busy%20year%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20its%20focus%20on%20rights%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjharkhand-nia-raids-rupesh-kumar-singh-activists%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraided%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20independent%20journalist%20Rupesh%20Kumar%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20house%20at%20Ramgarh%20in%20Jharkhand.%20Singh%20was%20one%20of%20those%20whose%20phones%20were%20targeted%20with%20Pegasus%20spyware%20and%20is%20a%20petitioner%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20alleging%20violation%20of%20privacy.%20The%20agency%20also%20raided%20rights%20defenders%20Damodar%20Turi%2C%20convener%20of%20the%20Vishthapan%20Virodhi%20Jan%20Vikas%20Andolan%2C%20Bacha%20Singh%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Mazdoor%20Sangathan%20Samiti%20(MSS)%2C%20and%20the%20Anil%20Hansda%2C%20Dinesh%20Tudu%2C%20Nageshwar%20Mahato%20and%20Sanjay%20Turi%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20Jan%20Sangharsh%20Morcha.%20Documents%20and%20phones%20were%20seized%20and%20the%20NIA%20said%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cincriminating.%E2%80%9D%20Those%20raided%20alleged%20that%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20turn%20the%20focus%20away%20from%20the%20government%20as%20polls%20neared.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%2010%20days%20after%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20Ansar%20Indori%20appeared%20in%20a%20case%20challenging%20an%20FIR%20filed%20by%20the%20NIA%2C%20the%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fansar-indori-nia-raids-pfi-human-rights%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraided%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%203%3A%20The%20Delhi%20Police%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20day%20being%20called%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fmedia%2Fattack-on-free-press-indian-government%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eworst%20for%20a%20free%20press%20in%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2046%20journalists%20and%20commentators%20%E2%80%93%20some%20in%20their%2020s%2C%20some%20in%20their%2070s%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20and%20all%20associated%20with%20the%20independent%20news%20website%20NewsClick%2C%20were%20raided.%20Their%20homes%20were%20searched%2C%20their%20devices%20seized%20and%20they%20were%20interrogated%20for%20hours.%20Ostensibly%2C%20the%20case%20against%20them%20%E2%80%93%20which%20invoked%20sections%20of%20the%20anti-terrorism%20law%2C%20UAPA%20%E2%80%93%20was%20prompted%20by%20a%20report%20in%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20which%20alleged%20that%20one%20of%20its%20funders%2C%20a%20US%20businessman%2C%20was%20close%20to%20the%20Chinese%20government.%20However%2C%20most%20of%20the%20journalists%20raided%20were%20asked%20about%20their%20work%20on%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20NewsClick%20director%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20%E2%80%93%20who%20spent%20two%20years%20in%20jail%20during%20the%20Emergency%20in%20the%201970s%20%E2%80%93%20was%20arrested%2C%20along%20with%20another%20staffer%2C%20Amit%20Chakravorty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbarandbench%2Fstatus%2F1709810786544054758%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eopposed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Purkayastha%E2%80%99s%20plea%20seeking%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%20against%20him%20but%20has%20now%20been%20ordered%20by%20the%20court%20to%20part%20with%20it.%20In%20its%20absence%2C%20neither%20those%20arrested%2C%20nor%20those%20whose%20devices%20have%20been%20taken%2C%20have%20a%20clue%20about%20what%20the%20case%20against%20them%20is%20exactly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20did%20not%20oppose%20the%20bail%20plea%20of%20a%20BJP%20strongman%20MP%20with%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20molestation%20charges%20against%20him%20%E2%80%93%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh.%20To%20seek%20justice%20against%20Singh%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20famous%20wrestlers%20had%20sat%20in%20%3Ci%3Edharna%3C%2Fi%3E%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20been%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20criticism%20for%20a%20partisan%20investigation%20focusing%20disproportionately%20on%20dissenters.%20Its%20probe%20into%20the%202020%20northeast%20Delhi%20riots%20%E2%80%93%20during%20hearings%20of%20which%20it%20is%20routinely%20slammed%20by%20court%20judges%20for%20its%20negligence%20%E2%80%93%20has%20led%20to%20the%20jailing%20of%20activists%20and%20scholars.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20police%20has%20refused%20to%20register%20cases%20against%20Hindutva%20and%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20were%20caught%20on%20video%20inciting%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20is%20under%20the%20direct%20control%20of%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20under%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%204%3A%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%204%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fenforcement-directorate-conducts-searches-at-aap-mp-sanjay-singhs-house%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebegan%20raids%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20house%20early%20in%20the%20morning.%20Officials%20arrested%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20New%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%20in%20the%20evening.%20The%20ED%20has%20already%20jailed%20two%20of%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20leaders%2C%20Satyendar%20Jain%20and%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20both%20Delhi%20ministers%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20bail%20hearing%20on%20Thursday%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsupreme-court-manish-sisodia-cbi-ed-delhi-excise-policy-case-8970027%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Easked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20ED%20how%20it%20plans%20to%20sustain%20its%20charge%20of%20money%20laundering%20by%20Sisodia%20%E2%80%9Cfactually%20and%20legally%E2%80%9D%20when%20he%20did%20not%20come%20to%20possess%20the%20money%20allegedly%20paid%20as%20per%20its%20own%20submission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20day%20ago%2C%20the%20same%20bench%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Fwhy-aap-not-made-accused-in-liquor-policy-case-sc-to-ed%2Farticle67381788.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Easked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%2C%20if%20the%20the%20whole%20of%20the%20AAP%20was%20said%20to%20be%20the%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20liquor%20policy%20as%20the%20ED%20contended%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20neither%20an%20accused%20nor%20impleaded%20in%20the%20case.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20on%20October%205%20raided%20premises%20linked%20to%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Bengal%20cabinet%20minister%20Rathin%20Ghosh%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20recruitment%20scam.%20TMC%20is%20protesting%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20disbursal%20of%20MGNREGA%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20ED%20also%20raided%20Karnataka%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20R.M.%20Manjunath%20Gowda%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20scam%20at%20the%20Shivamogga%20District%20Cooperative%20Central%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20and%20its%20internal%20functioning%20have%20been%20in%20the%20news%20more%20than%20any%20other%20central%20agency%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20tenure%20of%20its%20chief%2C%20S.K.%20Mishra.%20In%20an%20unprecedented%20move%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsk-mishra-enforcement-directorate-fatf-evaluation%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epleaded%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20case%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%E2%80%93%20against%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20judgment%20%E2%80%93%20by%20reiterating%20its%20stand%20that%20Mishra%20was%20required%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20helm%20because%20of%20the%20global%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%E2%80%99s%20impending%20review.%20But%2C%20as%3Ci%3E%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsk-mishra-enforcement-directorate-fatf-evaluation%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20noted%20in%20an%20analysis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20a%20comparatively%20limited%20role%20in%20an%20FATF%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%E2%80%99s%20extraordinary%20attention%20to%20opposition%20leaders%20during%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20extended%20tenure%20has%20been%20chronicled%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftracking-the-ed-case-by-case-puzzling-questions-emerge-in-its-handling-of-opposition-leaders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ecase-by-case%20analysis%20by%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20what%20the%20ED%20is%20handling.%20In%20August%202021%2C%20the%20ED%20submitted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F122-sitting-ex-legislators-facing-laundering-cases-ed-tells-sc%2Farticleshow%2F85196602.cms%5C%22%3Ea%20list%20of%20122%20elected%20representatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20are%20currently%20being%20investigated%20for%20money%20laundering%20charges%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20When%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1027571%2Fhow-the-modi-government-has-weaponised-the-ed-to-go-after-indias-opposition%5C%22%3EScroll.in%20%3C%2Fa%3Esought%20details%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%20the%20ED%20declined%20to%20share%20them.%20However%2C%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F122-sitting-ex-legislators-facing-laundering-cases-ed-tells-sc%2Farticleshow%2F85196602.cms%5C%22%3Epublished%20a%20report%20featuring%2052%20names%20drawn%20from%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nearly%20all%20belonged%20to%20Opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fsince-2014-4-fold-jump-in-ed-cases-against-politicians-95-per-cent-are-from-opposition-8163060%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fi%3E%20further%20reported%20last%20year%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202014%2C%20there%20had%20been%20a%204-fold%20jump%20in%20ED%20cases%20against%20politicians.%2095%25%20were%20from%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%205%3A%20Income%20Tax%20department%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Income%20Tax%20department%20on%20Thursday%20conducted%20searches%20at%20about%2040%20locations%20linked%20to%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20MP%20S.%20Jagathrakshakan%20in%20Chennai%20and%20its%20suburbs.%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20Stalin%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20critics%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20was%20quick%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmkstalin%2Fstatus%2F1709820887061639295%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9CArresting%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20raiding%20DMK%20MP%20Jagathrakshakan%E2%80%99s%20home%20are%20clear%20examples%20of%20their%20misuse%20of%20independent%20investigating%20agencies%20for%20political%20ends%20against%20INDIA%20bloc%20leaders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20DMK%20leader%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%20V.%20Senthil%20Balaji%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case.%20Following%20this%2C%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20move%2C%20the%20governor%20of%20the%20state%2C%20T.N.%20Ravi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftn-governor-dismisses-dmk-minister-senthil-balaji-who-was-arrested-by-ed-from-cabinet%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esought%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20dismiss%20him%20from%20the%20council%20of%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20Income%20Tax%20officials%20also%20went%20to%20the%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20offices%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20just%20days%20after%20it%20released%20a%20documentary%20focusing%20on%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20