%20indictment.%20He%20also%20may%20have%20had%20a%20problem%20keeping%20potentially%20sensitive%20military%20matters%20to%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Trump%20left%20office%2C%20Australian%20billionaire%20and%20Mar-a-Lago%20Club%20member%20Anthony%20Pratt%20alleged%20in%20interviews%20with%20federal%20investigators%20that%20the%20former%20president%20disclosed%20details%20to%20him%20about%20US%20nuclear%20submarines%20around%20April%202021%2C%20anonymous%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fafter-white-house-trump-allegedly-discussed-potentially-sensitive%2Fstory%3Fid%3D103760456%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20said%20Pratt%20then%20went%20on%20to%20share%20that%20information%20with%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20foreign%20officials%2C%20some%20of%20his%20employees%2C%20and%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Trump%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider%20in%20an%20email%20that%20the%20leak%20of%20the%20disclosure%20is%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20and%20lacks%20%26quot%3Bproper%20context%20and%20relevant%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Department%20of%20Justice%20should%20investigate%20the%20criminal%20leaking%2C%20instead%20of%20perpetrating%20their%20baseless%20witch-hunts%20while%20knowing%20that%20President%20Trump%20did%20nothing%20wrong%2C%20has%20always%20insisted%20on%20truth%20and%20transparency%2C%20and%20acted%20in%20a%20proper%20manner%2C%20according%20to%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20details%2C%20according%20to%20ABC%20News'%20sources%2C%20revolved%20around%20the%20number%20of%20nuclear%20warheads%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-us-navy-nuclear-powered-submarines-dominate-the-seas-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20submarines%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20carry%20and%20how%20close%20they%20could%20get%20to%20a%20Russian%20submarine%20without%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20Trump%20relayed%20accurate%20information%2C%20but%20investigators%20have%20asked%20Pratt%20not%20to%20repeat%20it%20elsewhere%2C%20sources%20told%20ABC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Mar-a-Lago%20employee%20later%20alleged%20to%20investigators%20that%20he%20heard%20Pratt%20share%20the%20details%20with%20another%20person%20within%20minutes%20after%20his%20meeting%20with%20Trump%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ABC%20News%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20about%20Trump%20disclosing%20that%20information%20were%20shared%20with%20special%20counsel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspecial-counsel-jack-smith-americans-read-trump-federal-indictment-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJack%20Smith%3C%2Fa%3E's%20team.%20Smith%20is%20leading%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20investigation%20into%20Trump's%20handling%20of%20classified%20documents%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-kept-documents-so-sensitive-even-access-codes-secret-indictment-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop-secret%20national%20security%20information%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20indicted%20on%2040%20charges%20related%20to%20keeping%20national%20security%20secrets%2C%20obstructing%20investigations%2C%20and%20making%20false%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDetails%20of%20the%20reported%20discussions%20between%20Pratt%20and%20Trump%20were%20not%20included%20in%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20ABC%20News%20that%20Pratt%20claimed%20to%20investigators%20that%20he%20talked%20about%20his%20meeting%20with%20Trump%20with%20other%20people%20because%20he%20was%20pushing%20for%20a%20business%20partnership%20between%20Australia%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20potentially%20sensitive%20discussion%20around%20submarines%20came%20up%20after%20P