testimony%20to%20obtain%20information%20not%20already%20in%20the%20SEC's%20possession%20that%20is%20relevant%20to%20its%20lawful%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20SEC%20has%20followed%20all%20appropriate%20administrative%20steps%20required%20in%20seeking%20Musk's%20testimony.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20Musk's%20blatant%20refusal%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20SEC's%20subpoena%2C%20the%20SEC%20now%20asks%20the%20Court%20to%20intervene%20and%20compel%20Musk's%20compliance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Musk%20previously%20gave%20the%20SEC%20a%20half-day%20of%20testimony%20in%20July%20of%202022%20related%20to%20its%20investigation%2C%20the%20agency%20said%20it%20is%20requesting%20he%20submit%20to%20further%20questioning%20because%20of%20the%20huge%20amount%20of%20additional%20information%20it's%20received%20this%20year.%20The%20SEC%20has%20%26quot%3Bthousands%20of%20new%20documents%20from%20various%20parties%20as%20part%20of%20its%20investigation%2C%20including%20hundreds%20of%20new%20documents%20produced%20by%20Musk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SEC%20has%20not%20yet%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20question%20Musk%20about%20those%20documents%20and%20other%20substantial%20information%20it%20has%20obtained%20in%20its%20investigation%20since%20July%2027%2C%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said%20in%20its%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20back%20and%20forth%20with%20Musk's%20lawyer%2C%20who%20the%20SEC%20claims%20never%20objected%20to%20Musk%20sitting%20for%20another%20interview%2C%20the%20Tesla%20billionaire%20agreed%20to%20be%20questioned%20on%20Sept.%2015%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20He%20did%20not%20appear%20for%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20lawyer%2C%20Alex%20Spiro%2C%20told%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20SEC%20has%20already%20taken%20Mr.%20Musk's%20testimony%20multiple%20times%20in%20this%20misguided%20investigation%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20is%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Spurious%20ob