3Cp%3EChelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20Research%20employee%20testified%20Thursday%20about%20a%20tense%20exchange%20with%20SBF.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20bulletproof%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20said%20after%20discovering%20understated%20crypto%20losses%20at%20Alameda.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20incorrect%20balance%20sheet%20all%20started%20because%20of%20a%20programming%20bug%2C%20ex-employee%20Adam%20Yedidia%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20paddleball%20game%20at%20a%20Bahamas%20resort%2C%20where%20they%20shared%20a%20%2435%20million%20apartment%2C%20Adam%20Yedidia%20confronted%20his%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20months%20earlier%2C%20Yedidia%20had%20found%20a%20bug%20in%20the%20code%20he%20had%20written%20for%20FTX%2C%20the%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20where%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20developer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20code%20was%20supposed%20to%20automate%20the%20process%20of%20deposits%2C%20allowing%20customers%20to%20put%20money%20into%20their%20FTX%20accounts%20faster%20and%20alleviating%20employee%20workloads.%20But%20it%20introduced%20a%20major%20problem%3A%20In%20the%20internal%20ledger%20on%20FTX's%20exchange%2C%20the%20numbers%20for%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20a%20cryptocurrency%20hedge%20fund%2C%20were%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlameda%20Research%2C%20it%20was%20discovered%2C%20had%20%24500%20million%20more%20in%20liabilities%20than%20previously%20realized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20the%20bug%20was%20fixed%2C%20in%20June%202022%2C%20six%20months%20after%20its%20discovery%2C%20that%20figure%20had%20grown%20to%20%248%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20numbers%20seemed%20large%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Yedidia%20testified%20Thursday%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20downtown%20Manhattan.%20%26quot%3BIt%20concerned%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20hut%20between%20paddleball%20courts%2C%20Yedidia%20expressed%20his%20concern%20to%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20FTX%2C%20who%20also%20controlled%20Alameda%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20things%20OK%3F%26quot%3B%20Yadidia%20recalled%20asking%20Bankman-Fried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20had%20known%20each%20other%20for%20years%2C%20living%20together%20while%20students%20at%20MIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20that%20time%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20became%20SBF%2C%20a%20rockstar%20in%20the%20crypto%20world%20and%20a%20billionaire%20who%20comfortably%20rubbed%20shoulders%20with%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20fellow%20business%20titans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20appeared%20unusually%20nervous%20when%20responding%2C%20Yedidia%20testified%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20bulletproof%20last%20year%2C%20but%20we're%20not%20bulletproof%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20answered%2C%20according%20to%20Yedidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20%26quot%3Bwe%26quot%3B%20to%20mean%20both%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%2C%20Yedidia%20asked%20how%20long%20it%20would%20be%20until%20the%20companies%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bbulletproof%26quot%3B%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20said%20it%20could%20take%20between%20six%20months%20to%20three%20years%2C%20assuring%20his%20employee%20and%20friend%20that%20things%20would%20turn%20out%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20very%20large%20debt%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20that%20Alameda%20could%20repay%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Yedidia%20said%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20didn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sam%20bankman%20fried%20sbf%20court%20drawing%20illustration%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63a4b3307877e10018fd618e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20founder%20and%20former%20CEO%20of%20crypto%20currency%20exchange%20FTX%20in%20a%20courtroom%20last%20year.%3Cp%3EJane%20Rosenberg%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EYedidia%20testified%20about%20the%20incestuous%20financial%20relationship%20between%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFTX%20collapsed%20in%20November%202022%2C%20after%20the%20public%20learned%20about%20the%20unusual%20exposure%20between%20the%20exchange%20and%20Alameda%20Research.%20Alameda%20had%20used%20the%20deposits%20of%20ordinary%20FTX%20customers%20to%20repay%20the%20hedge%20fund's%20creditors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20events%20ultimately%20led%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-sbf-fraud-trial-ftx-explainer-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriminal%20charges%20against%20Bankman-Fried%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20faces%20seven%20counts%2C%20including%20alleged%20wire%20fraud%2C%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20securities%20fraud%2C%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20money%20laundering.%20Caroline%20Ellison%2C%20the%20now-former%20CEO%20of%20Alameda%20Research%20and%20Bankman-Fried's%20on-and-off%20girlfriend%2C%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20fraud%20charges%20for%20the%20same%20scheme%20and%20is%20cooperating%20with%20prosecutors%20against%20him%2C%20along%20with%20two%20other%20former%20FTX%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETestifying%20in%20Bankman-Fried's%20trial%20for%20a%20second%20day%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%2C%20Yedidia%20told%20jurors%20about%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20crypto%20mogul%2C%20and%20just%20how%20the%20finances%20between%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20Research%20became%20so%20intertwined%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYedidia%20and%20Bankman-Fried%20both%20lived%20together%20at%20MIT%2C%20where%20Yedidia%20majored%20in%20electrical%20engineering%2C%20computer%20science%2C%20and%20math%20as%20an%20undergraduate.%20Before%20pursuing%20a%20PhD%20at%20MIT%2C%20he%20briefly%20worked%20at%20Alameda%20Research%20as%20a%20trader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223563%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22adam%20yedidia%20sam%20bankman%20fried%20trial%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651f18809f7ca8b2bbdae9e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20FTX%20developer%20Adam%20Yedidia%20leaves%20after%20testifying%20during%20the%20trial%20of%20former%20FTX%20CEO%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20at%20Manhattan%20Federal%20Court%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202021%2C%20Yedidia%20began%20working%20for%20FTX%20as%20a%20programmer.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20FTX%20was%20establishing%20itself%20as%20a%20major%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20that%20would%20soon%20be%20worth%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars.%20Bankman-Fried%20was%20becoming%20a%20crypto%20power%20broker%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20throwing%20money%20into%20different%20causes%20and%20meeting%20with%20lawmakers%20to%20shape%20regulation%20of%20digital%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYedidia%20observed%20just%20how%20incestuous%20the%20two%20companies%20were.%20They%20shared%20an%20office%20and%20had%20some%20of%20the%20same%20executives.%20In%20the%20Bahamas%2C%20top%20employees%20and%20their%20significant%20others%20in%20both%20companies%20shared%20a%20%2435%20million%20penthouse%20apartment%20that%20Alameda%20Research%20paid%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20FTX%2C%20Yedidia%20was%20tasked%20with%20developing%20software%20that%20automated%20customer%20deposits%2C%20making%20the%20process%20it%20faster%20for%20FTX%20users%20and%20easier%20on%20employees%20who%20would%20otherwise%20have%20to%20do%20it%20manually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20on%20the%20program%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20FTX%20customer%20funds%20were%20held%20in%20an%20account%20owned%20by%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20rather%20than%20an%20account%20owned%20by%20FTX.%20Customers%20were%20never%20told%20that%20Alameda%20owned%20the%20account%2C%20he%20said.%20Eventually%2C%20FTX%20got%20its%20own%20bank%20account%20for%20customer%20deposits%2C%20but%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20funds%20remained%20in%20Alameda's%20account%20anyway%2C%20Yedidia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYedidia%20said%20the%20bug%20in%20FTX's%20code%20understated%20how%20much%20money%20Alameda%20owed%20to%20FTX%20customers.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20FTX's%20software%20thought%20Alameda%20Research%20was%20richer%20than%20it%20actually%20was.%20The%20balance%20was%20off%20by%20%24500%20million%20at%20the%20time%20the%20bug%20was%20discovered%2C%20in%20around%20December%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recognized%20this%20as%20a%20potential%20problem%20for%20FTX's%20customers.%20When%20he%20began%20testifying%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-trial-former-roommate-adam-yedidia-immunity-testimony-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EYedidia%20said%20he%20insisted%20on%20getting%20immunity%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20he%20believed%20he%20%26quot%3Bmay%20have%20unwittingly%20written%20code%20that%20contributed%20to%20the%20commission%20of%20a%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20told%20Yedidia%20to%20fix%20the%20bug.%20Sometime%20after%20that%2C%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20Ellison%2C%20and%20executives%20Gary%20Wang%20and%20Nishad%20Singh%20met%20in%20a%20conference%20room%20in%20FTX's%20office%20area%2C%20Yedidia%20testified.%20Singh%20later%20said%20the%20group%20made%20a%20full%20accounting%20of%20FTX%20and%20Alameda's%20assets%20and%20liabilities%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20Yedidia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20trusted%20Sam.%20I%20hoped%20that%20Sam%20and%20Caroline%20and%20others%20at%20Alameda%20would%20handle%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Yedidia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYedidia%20fixed%20the%20bug%20by%20June%202022%2C%20Yedidia%20said.%20By%20that%20time%20Alameda's%20understated%20liabilities%20on%20the%20FTX%20exchange%20had%20reached%20%248%20billion%2C%20he%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20months%20that%20followed%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20sought%20to%20raise%20funds%20from%20financiers%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20but%20the%20investments%20never%20materialized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20November%202022%2C%20FTX%20employees%20were%20resigning%20en%20masse.%20In%20a%20private%20text%20message%20on%20Signal%2C%20Yedida%20assured%20he%20would%20stick%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20you%2C%20Sam.%20I'm%20not%20going%20anywhere.%20Don't%20worry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20to%20Bankman-Fried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20Yedidia%20learned%20that%20Alameda%20Research%20had%20used%20the%20funds%20of%20FTX%20customers%2C%20meaning%20that%20customers%20may%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20withdraw%20their%20money%20from%20the%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20resigned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Alameda%20did%20seemed%20like%20a%20flagrantly%20wrong%20thing%20to%20have%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Yedidia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-trial-adam-yedidia-bug-8-billion-alameda-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696538074000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651c52ac617692f0d03df084%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-trial-adam-yedidia-bug-8-billion-alameda-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20Research%20employee%20Adam%20Yedidia%20told%20jurors%20about%20a%20tense%20exchange%20where%20SBF%20privately%20acknowledged%20his%20companies%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20bulletproof.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian%2CKatie%20Balevic)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-trial-adam-yedidia-bug-8-billion-alameda-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2