to%20launch%20his%20first%20restaurant%20to%20cater%20to%20travellers%20and%20truck%20drivers%20on%20National%20Highway%2058%20(NH-58)%2C%20little%20did%20he%20anticipate%20the%20social%20churning%20that%20was%20to%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EForty-three-year-old%20Waseem%2C%20along%20with%20his%20business%20partner%2C%20Pushpraj%20Singh%2C%20made%20a%20conscious%20choice%20to%20run%20two%20%E2%80%98pure%20vegetarian%E2%80%99%20eateries%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edhabas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20on%20the%20Delhi-Dehradun%20route%20in%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Muzaffarnagar%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20But%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20(pilgrimage)%20resulted%20in%20their%20business%20taking%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20is%20held%20every%20year%20during%20the%20onset%20of%20monsoon%20or%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esaawan%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20season%2C%20with%20lakhs%20of%20devotees%20of%20lord%20Shiva%20carrying%20holy%20water%20as%20offerings.%20Since%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20came%20to%20power%20with%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20leading%20the%20government%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20pilgrimage%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20growing%20religious%20polarisation.%20This%20includes%20district%20administrations%20in%20the%20state%20ordering%20the%20closure%20of%20meat%20shops%20along%20the%20route%20undertaken%20by%20pilgrims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20the%20earliest%20such%20diktats%20were%20issued%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Farchive%2Fin%2Fentry%2Fmeat-shops-kanwar-yatra_in_5c10fcace4b0ad8bf05cd156%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGhaziabad%20in%202016%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20by%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20government%2C%20and%20later%20in%20Dadri%20%E2%80%93%20the%20site%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthree-years-after-akhlaqs-murder-family-does-not-hope-to-return-to-dadri%5C%22%3Ecommunal%20lynching%20of%20Mohammad%20Akhlaq%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20after%20the%20BJP%20was%20elected%20to%20power%20in%202017.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Dadri%E2%80%99s%20far-right%20Hindu%20groups%20had%20been%20demanding%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20meat%20during%20the%20yatra%20since%202016%20itself%2C%20the%20shift%20in%20government%20from%20SP%20to%20the%20BJP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fdadri-kotwali-sho-orders-meat-shops-close-view-kanwar-yatra%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20saw%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20police%20administration%20finally%20enforcing%20a%20closure%20on%20meat%20shops%20in%20July%202017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContinuing%20this%20policy%20in%202023%2C%20the%20Adityanath%20administration%20ordered%20closure%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20meat%20starting%20July%204%2C%20with%20police%20officials%20citing%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmaintenance%20of%20peace%20between%20communities%E2%80%9D%20as%20reason%20for%20the%20same%2C%20even%20as%20several%20butchers%2C%20meat-sellers%20and%20restaurants%20claimed%20their%20livelihoods%20were%20impacted.%20In%20a%20first%2C%20as%20per%20locals%2C%20Muslim%20owners%20of%20even%20vegetarian%20restaurants%20and%20eateries%20across%20western%20UP%20now%20claim%20to%20be%20under%20threat%20since%20the%20yatra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20closure%20of%20meat%20shops%20has%20been%20happening%20for%20at%20least%20five%20or%20six%20years%20as%20far%20as%20I%20can%20recall.%20I%20understand%20it%20may%20hurt%20Hindu%20sentiments%2C%20but%20what%20have%20we%20done%20wrong%20when%20we%20only%20sell%20vegetarian%20items%3F%20The%20co-owner%20is%20a%20Thakur%20(Hindu)%2C%20our%20staff%20is%20almost%2090%25%20Hindu.%20But%20they%20even%20told%20us%20to%20shut%20shop%20along%20with%20the%20non-vegetraian%20places%20this%20time.%20I%E2%80%99m%20convinced%20this%20is%20just%20because%20of%20my%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Waseem%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20Sukhdev%20dhaba%20and%20%E2%80%98New%20Ganpati%20Tourist%20dhaba%20%E2%80%93%20Number%20One%E2%80%99%20on%20Muzaffarnagar%E2%80%99s%20highway.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05175637%2Funnamed-14.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221004%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05175637%2Funnamed-14.jpg%201004w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05175637%2Funnamed-14-300x125.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678474%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22419%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChandigarh%20Dhaba%20located%20on%20NH-58%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20was%20closed%20off%20during%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpure%20vegetarian%E2%80%9D%20hotel.%20Its%20owners%20are%20Muslims.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20communal%20campaign%20against%20Muslim%20restaurant%20owners%20using%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20names%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWaseem%E2%80%99s%20partner%20Pushpraj%20Singh%20pointed%20out%20how%20dozens%20of%20dhabas%20along%20NH-58%20were%20targeted%20after%20a%20campaign%20was%20launched%20by%20one%20Swami%20Yashveer%2C%20whose%20ashram%20is%20located%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20district%E2%80%99s%20Badhra%20block.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYashveer%2C%20along%20with%20his%20followers%2C%20created%20a%20social%20media%20campaign%20and%20circulated%20a%20list%20of%20dhabas%20with%20their%20exact%20location.%20Former%20pradhan%20(head)%20of%20the%20nearby%20Bajhedi%20village%2C%20and%20local%20SP%20member%20Sabir%20Hassan%2C%20also%20confirmed%20that%20Yashveer%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20circulated%20videos%20and%20a%20message%20was%20spread%20across%20WhatsApp%2C%20reaching%20out%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctour%20operators%2C%20cab%20and%20truck%20drivers%E2%80%99%20groups%2C%20so%20that%20they%20do%20not%20stop%20by%20these%20dhabas%20when%20they%20ferry%20passengers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20318px)%2085vw%2C%20318px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05175857%2Funnamed-15-225x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22318%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05175857%2Funnamed-15-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05175857%2Funnamed-15-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05175857%2Funnamed-15.jpg%20900w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678476%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22424%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20list%20of%20restaurants%20was%20circulated%20across%20social%20media%2C%20including%20WhatsApp%20groups%20of%20tour%20operators%2C%20cab%20and%20truck%20drivers%20to%20encourage%20a%20boycott.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Yashveer%20pointed%20out%20how%20the%20campaign%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20not%20intended%20to%20close%20eateries%20run%20by%20any%20community%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20announced%20this%20on%20September%2026%20again%2C%20and%20in%20the%20past%2C%20before%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20as%20well.%20We%20are%20only%20seeking%20transparency.%20If%20a%20restaurant%E2%80%99s%20owner%20is%20Muslim%2C%20keep%20a%20Muslim%20name%20for%20it.%20Our%20only%20demand%20is%20that%20they%20keep%20their%20real%20names%2C%20and%20do%20not%20fool%20innocent%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yashveer%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYashveer%20and%20a%20number%20of%20right-wing%20Hindu%20outfits%20publicly%20issued%20a%20letter%20in%20July%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20was%20accessed%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20many%20Muslim%20owners%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdhabas%2C%20mithai%20shops%20and%20tea%20stalls%E2%80%9D%20were%20naming%20their%20establishments%20after%20Hindu%20gods%20and%20goddesses.%20The%20letter%20appealed%20to%20Adityanath%20to%20take%20legal%20action%20against%20this%20practice%2C%20and%20claimed%20that%20Muslims%20could%20%E2%80%9Cspit%2C%20urinate%20and%20mix%20cow%20meat%20into%20food%20items%E2%80%9D%20without%20Hindu%20customers%20knowing%20about%20it.%20They%20hence%20demanded%20that%20Muslims%20stick%20to%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20names%E2%80%9D%20for%20their%20establishments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20being%20questioned%20by%20this%20reporter%20as%20to%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20law%20or%20social%20sanction%20forbidding%20any%20community%20from%20keeping%20names%20as%20per%20their%20choice%2C%20Yashveer%20brusquely%20pointed%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20customers%20also%20have%20a%20legal%20and%20constitutional%20right%20to%20know%20who%20is%20making%20their%20food%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20sub-divisional%20magistrate%20(SDM)%20Parmanand%20Jha%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20whether%20officials%20ordered%20the%20closure%20of%20dhabas%20on%20account%20of%20their%20names%2C%20but%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20name%20can%20be%20anything%2C%20the%20work%20should%20not%20be%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20being%20asked%20what%20law%20or%20provision%20bars%20Muslims%20from%20naming%20their%20establishment%20as%20they%20wish%2C%20Jha%20added%20that%20the%20issue%20was%20one%20of%20maintaining%20law%20and%20order%2C%20and%20public%20peace.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20someone%20names%20their%20restaurant%20as%20%E2%80%98Shiv%20Shakti%E2%80%99%20but%20serves%20biryani%20there%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20get%20vitiated%20and%20peace%20prevails%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20others%2C%20such%20as%20Shameem%20(who%20only%20wished%20to%20go%20by%20his%20first%20name)%2C%20co-owner%20of%20the%20Maharaja%20Bhoj%20dhaba%2C%20decried%20these%20claims%20and%20emphasised%20how%20even%20those%20selling%20%E2%80%9Conly%20vegetarian%E2%80%9D%20items%20were%20forced%20to%20close%20down%20during%20the%20yatra.%20The%20campaign%20also%20targeted%20%E2%80%9Creligion%20neutral%E2%80%9D%20names.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20ordered%20the%20closure%20of%20my%20dhaba%20which%20has%20a%20name%20called%20Maharaja%20Bhoj.%20Is%20Maharaja%20the%20name%20of%20any%20Hindu%20deity%3F%20What%20about%20Chandigarh%20dhaba%2C%20New%20Punjab%20Hotel%2C%20and%20other%20such%20dhabas%20run%20by%20Muslims%20which%20they%20shut%20during%20Kanwar%20Yatra%3F%20They%20were%20all%20religion%20neutral%20names.%20And%20we%20serve%20only%20vegetarian%20food.%20This%20is%20not%20about%20Hindu%20sentiments%20or%20Kanwar%20Yatra%2C%20this%20was%20clearly%20to%20target%20our%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shameem%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2027-year-old%20restaurateur%20%E2%80%93%20who%20used%20to%20run%20a%20similar%20%E2%80%98pure%20vegetarian%E2%80%99%20restaurant%20in%20Mussoorie%20earlier%20%E2%80%93%20said%20he%20had%20never%20experienced%20such%20treatment%20before%20this.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20dhaba%20was%20opened%20just%20recently%2C%20our%20operations%20here%20began%20in%20June.%20Before%20this%2C%20we%20ran%20a%20similar%20hotel%20in%20Mussoorie%20and%20have%20never%20faced%20such%20hostility.%20But%20this%20campaign%20has%20finished%20our%20business%20even%20before%20it%20could%20take%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05180205%2Funnamed-16.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05180205%2Funnamed-16.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05180205%2Funnamed-16-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05180205%2Funnamed-16-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678478%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20almost%20empty%20Maharaja%20Bhoj%20dhaba%2C%20where%20cooking%20and%20catering%20staff%20cool%20down%20amidst%20a%20decline%20in%20customers.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EShameem%20also%20spoke%20about%20how%20far-right%20groups%20circulated%20a%20WhatsApp%20message%20and%20Facebook%20videos%20that%20were%20later%20picked%20up%20by%20news%20media%20%E2%80%93%20including%20India%20TV%2C%20a%20national%20channel.%20He%20also%20stressed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cno%20law%2C%20nor%20any%20constitutional%20provision%E2%80%9D%20prevented%20them%20or%20anyone%20else%20from%20keeping%20names%20as%20per%20their%20choice.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20many%20Muslims%20actually%20keep%20such%20names%20because%20we%20know%20that%20discrimination%20exists.%20Would%20you%20go%20to%20an%20Abdullah%20dhaba%2C%20or%20a%20Ganpati%20dhaba%20if%20you%20want%20a%20simple%20vegetarian%20meal%3F%20Unfortunately%2C%20if%20people%20hear%20a%20name%20like%20Abdullah%20dhaba%20or%20Qadir%20tea%20stall%2C%20they%20immediately%20associate%20that%20with%20meat%20and%20non-vegetarian%20food%2C%20and%20so%20most%20people%20never%20go%20there.%20What%20is%20wrong%20in%20keeping%20any%20name%2C%20as%20long%20as%20what%20we%20serve%20respects%20persons%20of%20all%20faiths%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20Muslim%20restaurateurs%20across%20the%20state%20have%20been%20targeted%20repeatedly%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20campaign%20to%20bar%20Muslim-owned%20restaurants%20from%20selling%20even%20vegetarian%20food%20isn%E2%80%99t%20limited%20to%20Muzaffarnagar%20alone.%20Across%20UP%2C%20reports%20highlight%20how%20Muslim%20restaurateurs%20have%20faced%20threats%20and%20intimidation%2C%20both%20for%20selling%20meat%20and%20even%20otherwise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20365px)%2085vw%2C%20365px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05180434%2Funnamed-7-300x188.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22365%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05180434%2Funnamed-7-300x188.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05180434%2Funnamed-7-1024x640.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05180434%2Funnamed-7.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678485%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22229%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENational%20media%20covered%20the%20news%20of%20these%20Muslim-owned%20eateries%20being%20shut%20down%20with%20incendiary%20headlines%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9CMiyabhai%20exposed!%E2%80%9D.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20from%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20180%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20in%20Sambhal%2C%20Tabish%20Hussain%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehow%20both%20he%20and%20his%20father%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Ctargeted%E2%80%9D%20twice.%20Last%20year%2C%20Hussain%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%2059-year-old%20Talib%20Hussain%2C%20spent%20close%20to%20two%20weeks%20in%20prison%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments%20after%20they%20sold%20some%20chicken%20wrapped%20in%20a%20newspaper%20that%20had%20images%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20printed%20on%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20registered%20against%20Talib%20also%20claimed%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20attack%20the%20police%20with%20a%20knife%2C%20and%20charged%20him%20with%20sections%20including%20295A%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edeliberate%20and%20malicious%20acts%2C%20that%20are%20intended%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings%20of%20any%20class%20by%20insulting%20its%20religion%20or%20religious%20beliefs)%2C%20153A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20residence)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20307%20(attempt%20to%20commit%20murder)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20Talib%20is%20out%20on%20bail%20today%2C%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20ordeal%20has%20not%20ended.%20Their%20restaurant%20%E2%80%98Mehak%E2%80%99%20has%20taken%20a%20hit%20ever%20since.%20Tabish%20pointed%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdespite%20our%20decision%20to%20sell%20only%20vegetarian%20dishes%20this%20year%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esaawan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(monsoons)%20began%E2%80%9D%2C%20police%20officials%20ordered%20that%20he%20shut%20shop%20ahead%20of%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Tabish%20said%20that%20his%20business%20has%20resumed%2C%20nearly%2030%20to%2040%20other%20such%20establishments%20in%20the%20area%20were%20forced%20to%20shut%20down%20during%20the%20two%20months%20of%20saawan%20when%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20takes%20place.%20He%20also%20informed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cno%20official%20notice%20or%20order%E2%80%9D%20was%20given%20to%20them%20when%20the%20police%20forced%20their%20establishments%20to%20close.%20The%20region%E2%80%99s%20district%20magistrate%2C%20Manish%20Bansal%2C%20even%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fground-reports%2Fno-written-order-but-up-police-has-shut-muslim-restaurants-in-sambhal-for-kanwar-yatra%2F1689476%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Print%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20no%20official%20orders%20to%20shut%20non-vegetarian%20(let%20alone%20vegetarian)%20restaurants%20had%20been%20issued%20from%20his%20office.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuslim-owned%20food%20establishments%20have%20been%20facing%20a%20similar%20plight%20in%20Mathura%20since%202021.%20The%20city%E2%80%99s%20association%20with%20the%20Hindu%20god%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20birthplace%20led%20to%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20push%20to%20ban%20the%20sale%20of%20meat%20and%20liquor.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2031%2C%202021%2C%20authorities%20banned%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20sale%20of%20meat%20and%20liquor%20in%2022%20municipal%20wards%20which%20were%20within%20a%201.5%20kilometre%20radius%20of%20the%20Shri%20Krishna%20Janmasthan%20Temple.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newarab.com%2Ffeatures%2Findias-holy-city-bjp-sponsored-meat-ban-targets-muslims%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMultiple%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fscared-to-buy-eat-meat-muslims-in-mathura-after-arrests-on-suspicion-of-cow-slaughter%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%20noted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20how%20the%20move%20has%20impacted%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20Muslim%20meat%20sellers%2C%20restaurateurs%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehotel%20owners.%20Even%20Muslims%20selling%20vegetarian%20items%20weren%E2%80%99t%20spared.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIrfan%2C%20a%20dosa%20vendor%2C%20said%20that%20in%20August%202021%2C%20%E2%80%9Cclose%20to%20ten%20men%E2%80%9D%20attacked%20his%20cart%2C%20despite%20him%20selling%20%E2%80%9Cpure%20vegetarian%E2%80%9D%20food.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20He%20claimed%20that%20they%20had%20an%20issue%20with%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Shrinath%20Dosa%20Corner%E2%80%99%2C%20citing%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20god%E2%80%99s%20name%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20he%20ought%20to%20use%20a%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20name%E2%80%9D%20to%20run%20his%20dosa%20joint.%20Under%20pressure%2C%20he%20changed%20the%20stall%E2%80%99s%20name%20to%20%E2%80%98American%20Dosa%20Corner%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwide-range-of-fears-new-indias-muslims-have%5C%22%3EHow%20Are%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslims%20Feeling%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOthers%20such%20as%20Mohammad%20Zameel%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fagra%2Fto-stay-afloat-in-mathura-muslim-hotelier-replaces-staff-with-hindus%2Farticleshow%2F91929844.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rechristened%20the%20%E2%80%98Taj%20Hotel%E2%80%99%20running%20in%20Mathura%E2%80%99s%20Daresi%20road%20since%201974%20to%20%E2%80%98Royal%20Family%20Restaurant%E2%80%99%20in%20December%202021.%20Zameel%E2%80%99s%20establishment%2C%20which%20earlier%20sold%20meat%20dishes%2C%20now%20serves%20a%20vegetarian%20menu.%20He%20even%20replaced%20his%20Muslim%20cooking%20and%20catering%20staff%20with%20Hindus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20many%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20have%20removed%20their%20names%20from%20GST%20registration%20and%20other%20official%20paperwork.%20Nazim%20Tyagi%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20restaurant%20owner%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20year%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20targeting%20vegetarian%20restaurants%20feels%20inevitable%20because%20of%20our%20religious%20identity.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20whether%20we%20sell%20only%20vegetarian%20items%20and%20have%20an%20all-Hindu%20staff.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETyagi%2C%20who%20partnered%20with%20one%20Mohammad%20Yusuf%2C%20alias%20%E2%80%98Guddu%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20open%20the%20locally%20famous%20Punjabi%20New%20Star%20Shuddh%20Dhaba%2C%20found%20his%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20list%20of%20dhabas%20run%20by%20Muslims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20not%20using%20any%20Hindu%20deity%E2%80%99s%20name%20for%20their%20establishment%2C%20both%20Tyagi%20and%20Yusuf%20were%20subject%20to%20the%20communal%20campaign%20on%20account%20of%20their%20religious%20identity.%20Today%2C%20he%20rues%20having%20to%20change%20%E2%80%9Call%20our%20paperwork%E2%80%9D%20to%20add%20one%20Sonu%20Pal%E2%80%99s%20name%20on%20their%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20registration%20documents.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20the%20owner%2C%20but%20this%20year%20I%20decided%20to%20put%20his%20name%20instead%20of%20mine%20on%20all%20our%20documents.%20Even%20the%20digital%20payments%2C%20phone%20number%20on%20the%20display%20board%20outside%2C%20GST%20registration%2C%20all%20of%20it%20are%20in%20his%20name%20now.%E2%80%9D%20While%20Pal%20has%20taken%20ownership%20without%20any%20qualms%2C%20Tyagi%20feels%20defeated%20that%20it%20has%20come%20to%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20cross-section%20of%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3Elivelihoods%20destroyed%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA*%20(who%20requested%20that%20his%20name%20be%20kept%20anonymous)%2C%20the%20co-owner%20of%20Chandigarh%20dhaba%20on%20NH-58%20is%20now%20struggling%20to%20pay%20his%20staff.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20this%20hate%20campaign%2C%20our%20eatery%20would%20have%20sales%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20on%20a%20good%20day.%20Now%2C%20there%20are%20barely%20any%20customers.%20I%20had%20ten%20people%20employed%2C%20and%20only%20five%20remain%20now%20because%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20keep%20the%20rest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20and%20his%20brother%20come%20from%20a%20Muslim%20family%20and%20said%20that%20they%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20restaurant%20business%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20the%20recent%20move%20was%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%E2%80%9D.%20He%20pointed%20out%20how%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20Hindus%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20mostly%20working%20class%20Hindu%20staff%20in%20our%20dhabas%E2%80%9D%20were%20also%20hit.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnew-india-muslim-bigotry-cosmopolitan-privilege%5C%22%3EIn%20New%20India%2C%20a%20Muslim%20Rose%20Smells%20Different%20From%20a%20Hindu%20Rose%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20national%20media%20and%20social%20media%20keep%20replaying%20the%20videos%20of%20Swami%20Yashveer%20and%20his%20followers%20saying%20that%20Muslims%20spit%2C%20urinate%20and%20mix%20cow%20meat%20into%20their%20food%2C%20then%20obviously%20it%20will%20affect%20our%20establishments.%20But%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20realise%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20the%20Hindus%20who%E2%80%99ve%20suffered%20because%20most%20of%20those%20who%20work%20in%20these%20vegetarian%20dhabas%20are%20Hindus.%20They%20would%20earn%20Rs%20200-300%20a%20day%2C%20now%20many%20are%20completely%20destitute%20or%20jobless%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWaseem%20Ahmed%2C%20the%20co-owner%20of%20Sukhdev%20Dhaba%20and%20New%20Ganpati%20Tourist%20Dhaba%2C%20concurred.%20Running%20the%20New%20Ganpati%20hotel%20for%20over%20eight%20years%2C%20Ahmed%20feels%20that%20this%20time%20things%20were%20different.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20some%2015%20or%2016%20men%20working%20with%20us%20in%20Ganpati%20dhaba%20until%20last%20year%3B%20most%20of%20them%20were%20Hindus.%20Now%20my%20staff%20is%20reduced%20to%20just%20six%20or%20seven%20men.%20In%20Sukhdev%2C%20we%20have%20reduced%20our%20staff%20from%2030%20to%2035%20employees%20to%2015%20or%2016.%20Sales%20have%20also%20fallen%20by%20more%20than%20half%20of%20what%20they%20used%20to%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOthers%20such%20as%20Punjabi%20New%20Star%20dhaba%E2%80%99s%20Sonu%20Pal%20point%20out%20how%20their%20staff%20of%20nearly%2035%20men%20have%20suffered%20over%20the%20past%20two%20months.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20made%20preparations%20in%20advance%20for%20the%20monsoon%20season%20but%20because%20of%20being%20shut%20this%20time%2C%20we%20lost%20at%20least%20Rs%203%20to%204%20lakhs%20worth%20of%20supplies.%E2%80%9D%20Tyagi%20added%20that%20their%20dhaba%20was%20shut%20for%20%E2%80%9Cat%20least%2020%20days%2C%20from%20July%201%20to%2020%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20restaurateurs%2C%20the%20damage%20caused%20to%20people%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20because%20of%20the%20forced%20closure%20has%20been%20the%20most%20unnerving.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fapp%3Ddesktop%26v%3DumnZUn4KudI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20Now%20ran%20a%20programme%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20featuring%20our%20dhabas%20in%20the%20background%2C%20with%20the%20ticker%20saying%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Miyaanbhai%20Exposed%E2%80%99.%20Our%20businesses%20have%20been%20humiliated%20in%20front%20of%20people%20nationwide%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chandigarh%20dhaba%E2%80%99s%20owner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOthers%20like%20Waseem%20Ahmed%20are%20now%20looking%20to%20quietly%20exit%20from%20the%20business.%20%E2%80%9COur%20GST%20registration%20for%20the%20hotels%2C%20digital%20payment%20identity%2C%20rental%20documents%2C%20everything%20is%20now%20in%20my%20partner%20Pushpraj%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20has%20been%20considering%20moving%20base%20to%20a%20foreign%20country%20like%20Thailand.%20%E2%80%9CI%20entered%20this%20business%20after%20seeing%20the%20prospects.%20But%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20my%20children%20to%20suffer%20or%20be%20deprived%20of%20pursuing%20opportunities%20just%20because%20of%20their%20name.%20If%20a%20Muslim%20isn%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20sell%20even%20vegetarian%20food%20in%20this%20environment%2C%20what%20should%20we%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E*Name%20changed%20to%20maintain%20anonymity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESabah%20Gurmat%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20This%20story%20is%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20series%20on%20the%20socio-economic%20decline%20of%20industries%20and%20businesses%20led%20by%20Muslims.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EReporting%20for%20her%20article%20was%20supported%20by%20the%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Media%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Howard%20G.%20Buffett%20Fund%20for%20Women%20Journalists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696516016000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05175005%2Funnamed-13.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdoesnt-matter-if-we-sell-vegetarian-food-how-ups-muslim-restaurant-owners-are-losing-livelihood%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dozens%20of%20dhabas%20along%20NH-58%20were%20reportedly%20targeted%20after%20a%20campaign%20was%20launched%20by%20one%20Swami%20Yashveer%20to%20advocate%20for%20the%20boycott%20of%20Muslim-owned%20eateries%20during%20the%20Kanwar%20Yatra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdoesnt-matter-if-we-sell-vegetarian-food-how-ups-muslim-restaurant-owners-are-losing-livelihood%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Why%20Me%3F%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20Patients%20of%20Spinal%20Muscular%20Atrophy%20Want%20India%20to%20Learn%20About%20Their%20Condition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20say%20that%20I%20could%20walk%20as%20a%20toddler%20but%20over%20time%2C%20I%20started%20losing%20balance.%20I%20would%20fall%20over%2C%20my%20spine%20became%20slightly%20curved%2C%20and%20I%20needed%20assistance%20with%20daily%20activities.%20My%20parents%20ran%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20to%20get%20a%20diagnosis%2C%E2%80%9D%20recounts%20Priya%20Srivastava%2C%20a%20Lucknow-based%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327878%2Fsejal-shah-mariposa-foundation-shares-lessons-for-raising-a-child-with-disability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20disability%20rights%20activist%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20has%20Spinal%20Muscular%20Atrophy%20(SMA)%20Type-II.%20Such%20is%20the%20story%20of%20many%20people%20with%20the%20rare%2C%20progressive%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20when%2014-month-old%20Roha%20began%20experiencing%20trouble%20breathing%2C%20her%20parents%20rushed%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20another%20town.%20After%20two%20weeks%2C%20multiple%20tests%20and%20misdiagnoses%20later%2C%20they%20were%20shattered%20to%20know%20that%20their%20little%20daughter%20had%20the%20fatal%20illness.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20they%20heard%20of%20SMA%20and%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20meant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%20(RPwD%20Act%2C%202016)%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20include%20SMA%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20not%20much%20awareness%20of%20the%20condition%20even%20among%20medical%20professionals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKaran%20Shah%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20canine%20and%20feline%20behaviourist%2C%20was%20misdiagnosed%20with%20