is%20a%20specialist%20in%20South%20Asian%20history%20but%20his%20work%20spans%20urban%20geographies%2C%20colonial%20history%2C%20post-colonial%20theory%2C%20urban%20stuff%20and%20the%20history%20of%20science.%20He%20has%20innumerable%20books%20to%20his%20credit.%20I%20have%20read%20some%20of%20them.%20I%20have%20been%20deeply%20envious%20of%20others%2C%20hoping%20that%20I%E2%80%99d%20written%20parts%20of%20some%20of%20those.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%2C%20I%20think%20we%20are%20really%20concerned%20here%20with%20his%20latest%20work%2C%20which%20is%20a%20very%20interesting%20and%20important%20work%20that%20comes%20from%20a%20time%20when%20professor%20Gyan%20Prakash%20has%20an%20experience%20of%20it%20as%20somebody%20living%20through%20the%20times%20and%20also%20has%20cast%20sort%20of%20a%20scholarly%20lens%20and%20gaze%20on%20it.%20I%20am%20referring%20to%20the%20book%20%3Ci%3EEmergency%20Chronicles%3A%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Democracy%E2%80%99s%20Turning%20Point.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProf%20Gyan%20Prakash%2C%20welcome%20to%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThank%20you%20Seema.%20And%20thank%20you%20for%20that%20very%20generous%20introduction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FPe6uCBXHWYg%3Fsi%3DsJW4bZA5sZi6Tdx9%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%2C%20it%20was%20a%20very%20limited%20one.%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20to%20go%20on!%20(Smiles)%20So%20you%E2%80%99ve%20written%20%3Ci%3EEmergency%20Chronicles%3C%2Fi%3E%20%E2%80%93%20as%20I%20said%20because%20you%20were%20actually%20there%20and%20kind%20of%20bore%20witness%20to%20what%20was%20happening.%20And%20you%E2%80%99ve%20also%20looked%20at%20it%20as%20a%20scholar%20and%20as%20a%20historian.%20The%20book%20came%20out%20in%202018.%20There%20is%20a%20certain%20character%20there%20called%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20who%20is%20almost%20like%20a%20lynchpin%20of%20the%20argument%20or%20at%20least%20a%20very%2C%20very%20important%20symbol%20when%20you%20explain%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20Emergency.%20So%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20you%20to%20kind%20of%20dwell%20on%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20then%20in%201975%20and%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20with%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20now%20that%20he%20has%20been%20arrested%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA).%20He%E2%80%99s%20the%20editor%20of%20the%20news%20portal%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20under%20arrest%20as%20we%20speak%20under%20an%20Act%20which%20is%20meant%20to%20stop%20terrorism%20in%20the%20country.%20So%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20read%20a%20little%20bit%20from%20your%20book%20with%20your%20permission%2C%20professor%20Gyan%20Prakash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20you%20talk%20about%20when%20Prabir%20was%20a%20student%20at%20JNU.%20He%20is%20sitting%20there%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20waiting%20for%20his%20colleagues%2C%20comrades%2C%20and%20friends%20to%20join%20them%20briefly%20before%20they%20can%20start%20walking%20to%20the%20library.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CAround%2010%3A00%20a.m.%20a%20black%20car%20drove%20through%20the%20main%20gate%2C%20turned%20left%20and%20continued%20toward%20the%20School%20of%20Languages.%20It%20was%20an%20ambassador%2C%20one%20of%20the%20three%20automobile%20models%20manufactured%20in%20India%20and%20one%20invariably%20used%20by%20officials.%20At%20the%20wheel%20was%20a%20physically%20imposing%20sick%20DIG-%20Deputy%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Delhi%20police%2C%20PS%20Bhinder.%20With%20him%20were%20TR%20Anand%2C%20the%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%20and%20two%20constables%20all%20in%20plain%20clothes.%20The%20car%20stopped%20near%20the%20students.%20Bhinder%20got%20out%2C%20walked%20over%20to%20Prabir%20and%20asked%20%E2%80%98Are%20you%20Devi%20Prasad%20Tripathi%3F%E2%80%9D%20Prabir%20replied%20that%20he%20was%20not.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20next%20moment%20he%20found%20himself%20being%20pushed%20toward%20the%20car.%20His%20friends%20rushed%20to%20save%20him%20from%20the%20plainclothes%20men%20and%20momentarily%20succeeded%20in%20pulling%20him%20away%20from%20the%20car.%20Prabir%20also%20resisted%20but%20the%20policeman%20beat%20back%20the%20students%2C%20lifted%20Prabir%20off%20his%20feet%20and%20shoved%20him%20into%20the%20rear%20seat.%20Prabir%E2%80%99s%20friends%20screamed%20for%20help%2C%20one%20of%20them%20rushed%20to%20the%20driver%E2%80%99s%20side%20and%20tried%20to%20snatch%20the%20car%20keys%20from%20the%20ignition%20but%20Bhinder%20came%20from%20behind%2C%20grabbed%20her%20hair%20and%20hurled%20her%20to%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EA%20flicker%20of%20hope%20rose%20momentarily%20in%20Prabir%20when%20he%20locked%20eyes%20with%20a%20small%20group%20of%20students%20standing%20nearby%20witnessing%20his%20ordeal%20but%20it%20died%20as%20quickly%20as%20it%20had%20risen%20when%20he%20saw%20them%20turn%20away%20with%20fear%20in%20their%20eyes.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EWith%20the%20constables%20holding%20the%20slender%20long%20frame%20of%20a%20struggling%20Prabir%20in%20the%20rear%20seat%2C%20his%20legs%20jutting%20out%20of%20the%20open%20door%2C%20the%20car%20reversed%20in%20high%20speed%2C%20turned%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20entry%20gate%20and%20raced%20out%20of%20the%20campus.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20as%20we%20know%2C%20Prabir%20after%20that%20goes%20on%20to%20serve%20a%20fairly%20long%20sentence%2C%20a%20few%20other%20of%20his%20fellow%20students%20%E2%80%93%20some%20of%20whom%20are%20now%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20were%20also%20arrested.%20So%20tell%20us%20about%20Prabir%20then%20and%20why%20is%20he%20the%20star%20of%20this%20book%2C%20if%20I%20may%20use%20that%20phrase%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20him%20very%20well%20but%20I%20knew%20him%20when%20I%20was%20a%20student%20at%20JNU.%20While%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20actually%20present%20at%20this%20incident%20of%20Bhinder%20grabbing%20him%20but%20when%20I%20came%20down%20from%20my%20hostel%20room%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20I%20heard%20about%20it.%20So%20%5BI%20revisited%20it%5D%20when%20I%20started%20researching%20the%20Emergency%2C%20%5Bespecially%5D%20since%20JNU%20had%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20many%20of%20these%20arrests%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20include%20what%20happened%20in%20JNU%20as%20part%20of%20the%20story.%20Once%20I%20made%20that%20decision%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Prabir%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20you%20know%2C%20jumped%20out.%20Then%20I%20also%20found%20that%20in%20the%20Shah%20Commission%20Report%2C%20there%20were%20a%20considerable%20number%20of%2C%20quite%20a%20few%20pages%20devoted%20to%20his%20particular%20case.%20Then%20in%20the%20actual%20depositions%20%E2%80%93%20not%20in%20the%20report%20itself%2C%20but%20in%20the%20actual%20depositions%20%E2%80%93%20I%20found%20a%20lot%20more%20material.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20what%20happened%20to%20Prabir%20at%20that%20time%20was%20terrible%20of%20course%2C%20but%20it%20compares%20nothing%20to%20what%E2%80%99s%20going%20on%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20looking%20at%20what%20had%20happened%20during%20the%20Emergency%2C%20Prabir%E2%80%99s%20case%20in%20a%20way%20encapsulates%20what%20I%20call%20in%20the%20book%20%E2%80%98unlawful%20suspension%20of%20the%20law%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20various%20laws%20that%20are%20on%20the%20books%20could%20be%20unlawfully%20invoked%20to%20put%20someone%20like%20him%20in%20prison.%20So%20as%20I%20researched%20his%20case%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20there%20was%20no%20warrant%20of%20arrest%20against%20him%20under%20MISA%20%5Bthe%20Maintenance%20of%20Internal%20Security%20Act%5D%20but%20once%20they%20had%20arrested%20him%2C%20they%20had%20to%20justify%20it%20somehow.%20So%20they%20basically%20intimidated%20the%20ADM%20%5Badditional%20district%20magistrate%5D%20to%20issue%20a%20warrant%20of%20arrest%20in%20his%20name.%20So%20in%20a%20way%2C%20that%20encapsulated%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20went%20on%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20I%20think%20he%20also%20became%20a%20kind%20of%20a%20thread%20through%20which%20I%20could%20tell%20the%20longer%20story%20of%20the%20Emergency%20because%20the%20Emergency%20happens%20against%20a%20background%20of%20student%20unrest%20and%20the%20student%20unrest%20of%20which%20Prabir%20was%20a%20part%20and%20an%20expression%20of%20the%20radical%20youth%20in%20the%2060s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EEmergency%2C%20if%20you%20just%20take%20it%20away%20from%20the%20immediate%20background%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20judgment%20%5Bwhich%20disqualified%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20precipitated%20the%20imposition%20of%20Emergency%5D%20but%20see%20it%20in%20a%20kind%20of%20broader%20frame%2C%20has%20to%20be%20placed%20against%20that%20context%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Estudent%20unrest%20and%20crisis%20in%20India%20in%20the%20late%2060s%20and%20early%2070s.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20himself%20being%20a%20product%20of%20that%20milieu%2C%20Prabir%E2%80%99s%20case%20then%20for%20me%20seemed%20like%20a%20very%20apt%20character%20through%20which%20the%20story%20of%20the%20emergency%20could%20be%20told.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600p