d%20they%20are%20now%20also%20trying%20to%20clear%20any%20dissent%20in%20social%20media%2C%20on%20the%20Internet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20surprising%20that%20they%E2%80%99ve%20gone%20after%20someone%20like%20Prabir%20at%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%20What%20we%20are%20witnessing%20now%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20a%20really%20totalitarian%20society%20in%20which%20every%20thought%20that%20deviates%20from%20the%20officially%20prescribed%20one%20is%20already%20suspect.%20So%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20potentially%20any%20human%20being%20who%20thinks%2C%20is%20a%20suspect%20in%20this%20regime.%20If%20you%20think%2C%20you%20can%20change%20your%20mind%2C%20you%20can%20think%20differently%2C%20you%20can%20express%20dissent%2C%20then%20simply%20your%20capacity%20to%20think%20and%20critique%20makes%20you%20a%20suspect.%20So%2C%20that%20is%20happening%20all%20over%2C%20I%20mean%20there%20is%20the%20case%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-police-arrest-teesta-setalvad-activist-who-pursued-2002-riots-case-against-modi%5C%22%3ETeesta%20%5BSetalvad%5D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbhima-koregaon-16-must-not-be-forgotten%5C%22%3E%5Bthe%20case%20of%20%5D%20Bhima%20Koregaon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20mean%20there%20are%20so%20many%20examples%20where%20you%20can%20see%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20aspect%20of%20this%2C%20which%20is%20also%20in%20a%20way%20different%20from%20the%20Emergency%20and%20is%20far%20graver%2C%20is%20to%20really%20achieve%20total%20domination%20through%20killing%20the%20juridical%20persona%20in%20a%20human%20being%20or%20in%20a%20citizen.%20And%20you%20do%20that%20by%20creating%20a%20system%20of%20law%20that%20is%20outside%20the%20normal%20penal%20system.%20So%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20file%20an%20FIR%2C%20you%20know%2C%20not%20charge%20him%20with%20kind%20of%20a%20normal%20criminal%20procedure%20but%20you%20charge%20him%20through%20UAPA%2C%20which%20creates%20a%20completely%20different%20sort%20of%20circle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%E2%80%99m%20not%20being%20hyperbolic%20but%20you%20know%20it%20is%20comparable%20to%20the%20way%20in%20which%20the%20concentration%20camps%20functioned.%20The%20concentration%20camp%20was%20outside%20the%20normal%20penal%20system%2C%20people%20who%20went%20there%20had%20no%20rights.%20They%20were%20outside%20any%20kind%20of%20juridical%20system%2C%20any%20protection%20of%20Law.%20And%20so%20you%20now%20create%20a%20criminal%2C%20you%20create%20a%20terrorist%20by%20completely%20killing%20all%20the%20kind%20of%20juridical%20protection%20that%20a%20citizen%20or%20human%20being%20has%20under%20a%20system%20of%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20if%20you%20think%20of%20these%20two%20aspects%20%E2%80%93%20every%20thought%20is%20suspect%2C%20every%20human%20being%20by%20his%20very%20capacity%20to%20think%20is%20a%20suspect%3B%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20this%20system%20of%20law%20that%20is%20outside%20the%20normal%20penal%20system%20%E2%80%93%20these%20point%20to%20a%20form%20of%20autocracy%20that%20Indira%20Gandhi%20never%20achieved%20during%20the%20Emergency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBad%20enough%20though%20it%20was%20for%20Prabir%20to%20be%20arrested%20without%20any%20reason.%20It%20was%20very%20different%20from%20being%20arrested%20under%20UAPA%2C%20where%20you%20know%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20protection%20of%20law%20at%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20two%20things%20you%20said%E2%80%A6%20%E2%80%98I%20think%20therefore%20I%20am%E2%80%99%20now%20turns%20into%20%E2%80%98I%20think%20therefore%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20suspect%E2%80%99.%20That%20kind%20of%20transformation%20has%20been%20effected.%20And%20number%20two%2C%20the%20way%20the%20law%20is%20kind%20of%20spun%20around%20a%20person%20whom%20they%20want%20to%20criminalise%20or%20put%20away.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20is%20that%20also%20the%20distinct%20difference%20from%20the%20Emergency%3F%20Because%2C%20say%20in%20the%20Emergency%2C%20you%20were%20jailed%20for%20being%20a%20journalist%20which%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20happening%20in%20India%20too%20and%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20that.%20Just%20the%20act%20of%20reporting%20is%20in%20chargesheets%2C%20that%20you%20reported%20on%20a%20certain%20activity%20is%20enough%20to%20send%20you%20to%20prison.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20also%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20whatever%20happens%E2%80%A6%20you%20know%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20opposite%20of%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20whatever%20happens%20in%20Kashmir%20%3Ci%3Edoes%3C%2Fi%3E%20get%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%20You%20know%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20soon%20be%20subject%20to%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20there.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20do%20you%20think%20this%20is%20the%20fundamental%20way%20in%20which%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20different%20from%20the%20Emergency%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20censorship%20during%20the%20Emergency%20was%20in%20fact%20an%20expression%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20weakness%20%E2%80%93%20that%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20control%20the%20Press%20and%20so%20she%20censored%20it.%20Here%20they%20use%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecensorship%20controls%20but%20in%20addition%2C%20they%20own%20the%20media.%20So%20they%20actually%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20do%20it.%20But%20what%20do%20you%20do%20about%20these%20kinds%20of%20dissenting%20voices%20that%20pop%20up%20on%20the%20Internet%20or%20social%20media%20and%20so%20on%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20you%20create%20the%20system%20where%20any%20normal%20protection%20that%20you%20would%20get%20from%20the%20law%20is%20unavailable%20to%20you.%20So%20this%20is%20very%20different%20from%20what%20they%20did%20in%20Kashmir.%20Of%20course%2C%20in%20a%20way%20you%20could%20compare%20that%20to%20the%20Emergency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20think%20firstly%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20going%20on%20is%20very%20different%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98undeclared%20Emergency%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20because%20it%20actually%20minimises%20the%20graveness%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20going%20on%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F14183024%2FNarendra-Modi-Indira-Gandhi.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F14183024%2FNarendra-Modi-Indira-Gandhi.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F14183024%2FNarendra-Modi-Indira-Gandhi-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F14183024%2FNarendra-Modi-Indira-Gandhi-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F14183024%2FNarendra-Modi-Indira-Gandhi-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-279448%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20and%20Indira-Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYes.%20So%20you%E2%80%99ve%20spoken%20about%20it%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20again%20bring%20back%20the%20focus%20on%20Prabir.%20There%20was%20a%20very%20clear%20way%20in%20which%20people%20like%20Prabir%20threatened%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20regime%2C%20so%20they%20were%20picked%20up%20and%20put%20away%20%E2%80%93%20student%20unrest%20and%20all%20that.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20what%20way%20do%20people%20like%20Prabir%20hurt%20a%20government%20which%20has%20been%20elected%20twice%20with%20a%20pure%20majority%2C%20and%20which%20has%20more%20than%20300%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%3F%20There%20is%20a%20virtual%20cult%20kind%20of%20thing%20here.%20We%20had%20a%20G20%20summit%20recently%2C%20where%20we%20had%20at%20least%2020%20kinds%20of%20faces%20travelling%20to%20India%2C%20even%20if%20we%20forget%20about%20the%201.4%20billion%20Indian%20faces.%20But%20we%20had%20posters%20with%20just%20one%20face%20%E2%80%93%20you%20had%20just%20Mr%20Modi.%20We%20were%20kind%20of%20carpet-bombed%20with%20Mr%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20face%20even%20at%20G20.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20are%20people%20like%20Prabir%20even%20a%20threat%3F%20I%20mean%2C%20there%20are%20massive%20troll%20armies%20which%20aren%E2%80%99t%20even%20just%20trolls.%20They%20are%20baked%20into%20the%20official%20propaganda%20push%20that%20this%20government%20does%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20does%E2%80%A6%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F09%2F26%2Fhindu-nationalist-social-media-hate-campaign%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fi%3E%20has%20extensive%20pieces%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20that%2C%20others%20have%20reported%20on%20it%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Freport-details-how-army-used-fake-accounts-to-target-kashmiri-journalists-promote-narrative%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fi%3Ehas%20reported%20too%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20why%20are%20individuals%20a%20threat%20to%20such%20a%20big%20machine%20which%20also%20has%20the%20full%20power%20of%20the%20Indian%20State%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20fusion%20of%20these%20two%20things.%20Why%20should%20they%20be%20scared%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20I%20was%20just%20the%20other%20day%20rereading%20Hannah%20Arendt%20on%20totalitarianism%20and%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20she%20says%20is%20that%20in%20a%20totalitarian%20society%2C%20there%20are%20always%20non-totalitarian%20elements%20that%20are%20beyond%20the%20control%20of%20the%20totalitarians.%20And%20people%20in%20power%20are%20always%20aware%20that%20there%20is%20something%20that%20is%20not%20under%20their%20control.%20There%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20fear.%20I%20mean%20look%20at%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20news%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2022%2F10%2F13%2F3500-km-but-whos-watching-how-big-media-dropped-the-ball-in-its-coverage-of-bharat-jodo-yatra%5C%22%3Ecompletely%20blacked%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Indian%20media.%20We%20read%20about%20it%20here%20in%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20Danish%20media%2C%20European%20media!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20there%20is%20this%20constant%20fear%20in%20a%20totalitarian%20society%20and%20she%20writes%20about%20Hitler%20also%2C%20that%20in%20spite%20of%20all%20the%20power%20that%20he%20enjoyed%2C%20there%20was%20always%20this%20kind%20of%20lurking%20suspicion%20that%20there%20are%20non-totalitarian%20elements%20which%20are%20not%20completely%20under%20our%20control.%20So%20much%20of%20the%20propaganda%20is%20often%20directed%20at%20drawing%20those%20people%20who%20are%20not%20completely%20under%20its%20ideological%20indoctrination%20and%20those%20people%2C%20if%20they%20are%20not%20brought%20under%20completely%20in%20their%20ideology%2C%20then%20you%20use%20whatever%20state%20apparatus%20that%20you%20can%20against%20them.%20So%20in%20a%20way%20what%20she%20writes%20about%2C%20creates%20a%20kind%20of%20fictitious%20reality%20where%20people%20in%20power%20feel%20that%20they%20have%20absolute%20control%20even%20as%20they%20know%20that%20there%20are%20sections%20that%20are%20outside%20their%20control.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20paranoia%20that%20is%20built%20into%20these%20totalitarian%20regimes%20which%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20want%20to%20dominate%20and%20yet%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20fear%20that%20perhaps%20their%20control%20is%20not%20total.%20And%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20machine%20that%20keeps%20triggering%20more%20and%20more%20attempts%20at%20control.%20So%20by%20itself%2C%20you%20may%20think%20Prabir%20is%20not%20a%20threat.%20He%20was%20not%20a%20threat%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20threat%20to%20Modi%E2%80%A6%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20thinking%20of%20Prabir%20as%20such%2C%20but%20Prabir%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20a%20wider%20arena%20of%20achieving%20total%20control%20in%20which%20all%20of%20these%20things%20become%20reminders%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20control%20that%20they%20have.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20last%20two%20questions%2C%20professor%20Gyan%20Prakash.%20The%20tough%20one%20first.%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20journalist%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20hack%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20expected%20to%20know%20what%20happens%20other%20than%20immediate%20term%20or%20max%20medium%20term.%20You%E2%80%99re%20a%20historian%2C%20you%20studied%20longer%20spans.%20How%20does%20all%20this%20end%3F%20End%20it%20has%20to%2C%20but%20how%20do%20systems%20like%20these%20which%20are%20not%20an%20Emergency%2C%20which%20are%20totalitarian%2C%20which%20come%20in%20through%20the%20popular%20vote%2C%20which%20enjoy%20state%20power%2C%20which%20believe%20in%20focus%20and%20centralisation%2C%20how%20does%20it%20end%3F%20What%20does%20the%20last%20scene%20of%20this%20film%20look%20like%3F%20I%20can%20see%20you%20have%20%3Ci%3EBarsaat%3C%2Fi%3E%20poster%20behind%20you%2C%20but%20what%20would%20be%20the%20title%20of%20this%20film%3F%20How%E2%80%99s%20it%20going%20to%20end%3F%20It%20has%20to%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20the%20day%20after%20is%20the%20most%20important%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAha.%20The%20Day%20After.%20That%E2%80%99s%20also%20the%20name%20of%20a%20film%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E(Prof%20Gyan%20Prakash%20smiles)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20just%20had%2C%20actually%20last%20weekend%2C%20a%20seminar%20on%20democracy%20and%20transition.%20Most%20of%20the%20discussion%20was%20really%20about%20Eastern%20Europe%2C%20but%20this%20was%20the%20question.%20In%20Poland%2C%20there%20is%20an%20election%20coming%20up%20on%20October%2015.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20Polish%20scholars%20and%20scholars%20of%20Hungary%20and%20so%20on.%20The%20uppermost%20thing%20in%20their%20mind%20is%2C%20if%20by%20some%20great%20fortune%2C%20and%20it%20does%20seem%20possible%2C%20that%20they%20manage%20to%20defeat%20the%20ruling%20regime%20in%20Poland%2C%20what%20happens%20the%20day%20after%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20what%20these%20regimes%20have%20done%20%E2%80%93%20and%20as%20BJP%20has%20done%20in%20India%2C%20is%20to%20not%20only%20enact%20a%20series%20of%20laws%2C%20like%20the%20UAPA%20amendment%20in%202019%2C%20CAA%2C%20the%20whole%20host%20of%20things%20but%20also%20bring%20in%20various%20kinds%20of%20administrative%20practices%20%E2%80%93%20using%20the%20ED%2C%20using%20Income%20Tax%20departments%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20unleashed%20so%20many%20of%20these%20administrative%20machines%20that%20it%E2%80%99ll%20be%20very%20difficult%20for%20a%20regime%20that%20comes%20into%20power%20after%20them%20to%20undo%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20after%20this%20ends%E2%80%A6%20I%20think%20the%20first%20thing%20%5Babout%20when%5D%20it%20ends%20is%20hopefully%20in%202024.%20It%20ends%20with%20the%20INDIA%20%5Bopposition%20bloc%5D%20emerging%20victorious%20over%20the%20BJP.%20But%20I%20think%20the%20real%20challenge%20would%20be%20a)%20undoing%20all%20of%20these%20kinds%20of%20administrative%20things%20that%20they%20have%20done%2C%20and%20b)%20actually%20removing%20the%20poison%20that%20they%20have%20disseminated%20in%20the%20populace.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20what%E2%80%99s%20happened%20here%20is%20also%20so%20different%20from%20the%20Emergency.%20Indira%20Gandhi%20had%20the%20Youth%20Congress%20but%20the%20Youth%20Congress%20was%20nothing%20compared%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20ground%20troops%20that%20the%20RSS%20is%20able%20to%20deploy%20and%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20able%20to%20deploy%20and%20actually%20all%20these%20really%20poisonous%20and%20vitriolic%20ideologies%20that%20they%E2%80%99ve%20spread%20in%20the%20populace.%20I%20mean%2C%20things%20that%20you%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20say%20in%20polite%20society%20about%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20people%20feel%20free%20to%20say%20now.%20How%20do%20you%20put%20the%20genie%20back%20in%20the%20bottle%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20think%20those%20are%20the%20real%20challenges%20in%20thinking%20about%20what%20happens%20the%20day%20after.%20So%20the%20day%20itself%20is%20not%20as%20important%20as%20the%20day%20after%20I%20think.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOkay%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20very%20thoughtful%20and%20very%20guarded.%20And%20we%20must%20temper%20optimism%2C%20even%20when%20it%20all%20ends.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComing%20back%20to%20Prabir%2C%20professor%20Gyan%20Prakash.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20conversations%20with%20him%20about%20his%20jail%20friends%20then.%20A%20lot%20of%20them%20were%20Sangh%20leaders%2C%20senior%20important%20leaders%2C%20some%20of%20them%20went%20on%20to%20be%20presidents%20of%20the%20BJP%20(which%20didn%E2%80%99t%20exist%20then%2C%20there%20was%20only%20the%20Jana%20Sangh)%20there%20was%20the%20RSS.%20The%20RSS%20and%20their%20associates%20go%20on%20about%20the%20Emergency%20and%20the%20repression.%20They%20celebrated%2040%20years%20of%20its%20end%20recently.%20So%20much%20tamasha%2C%20how%20do%20you%20reconcile%20that%20with%2C%20at%20least%20in%20large%20part%2C%20aspiring%20to%20be%20this%20kind%20of%20autocrat%2C%20this%20despot%2C%20this%20love%20for%20being%20the%20supreme%20monarch%2C%20kind%20of%20despot%E2%80%A6%20wanting%20to%20self-anoint%20and%20self-appoint%20themselves%3F%20How%20do%20you%20square%20%5Bthis%5D%3F%20Or%20is%20there%20no%20contradiction%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20do%20remember%20talking%20to%20Prabir%20about%20his%20jail%20years%20and%20him%20being%20pretty%20friendly%20with%20them.%20These%20were%20his%20fellow%20detainees%2C%20many%20of%20them%20were%20in%20the%20RSS%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20were%20desperate%20to%20get%20out%20and%20desperate%20to%20sign%20on%20%3Cem%3Emaafi-namas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(letters%20of%20apology).%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20SFI%20and%20CPM%20shared%20a%20kind%20of%20common%20hatred%20for%20%5Bthe%20Congress%5D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20the%20Congress%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes.%20Now%20those%20same%20Jana%20Sangh%20people%20%E2%80%93%20now%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20RSS%20who%20used%20to%20speak%20about%2C%20regularly%20every%20Emergency%20anniversary%2C%20yeah%E2%80%A6%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYeah%2C%20very%20often.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20often%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20did%20this%E2%80%A6%20and%20the%20Congress%20did%20that.%E2%80%9D%20For%20them%20to%20become%20this%20kind%20of%20autocrat%2C%20there%20are%20two%20things%20I%20would%20say.%20One%20is%20that%20in%20a%20way%2C%20a%20certain%20predilection%20for%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20was%20already%20there%20in%20the%20RSS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYes%2C%20I%20think%20that%20is%20the%20bedrock%20of%20their%20ideology.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20and%20that%20Hindu%20Rashtra%2C%20not%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20majoritarianism%20but%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20kind%20of%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20So%20that%20was%20already%20there%20but%20I%20think%20there%20was%20a%20transformation%20in%20the%20BJP%20itself%20as%20a%20party%20after%202014%20under%20Modi%2C%20where%2C%20if%20you%20think%20of%20the%20BJP%20prior%20to%202014%2C%20there%20were%20a%20number%20of%20leaders.%20There%20was%20Advani%2C%20there%20was%20Arun%20Jaitley.%20You%20could%20think%20of%20%5BShivraj%20Singh%5D%20Chouhan%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20There%20were%20a%20number%20of%20leaders.%20It%20was%20kind%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98normal%E2%80%99%20political%20party%2C%20in%20that%20sense.%20All%20that%20changed%20after%202014%2C%20when%20Modi%20became%20the%20singular%20focus%20of%20the%20party.%20So%20that%20way%2C%20the%20party%20has%20changed%20and%20it%20also%20changed%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20it%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20create%20a%20party-state%20that%20it%20never%20had%20before.%20So%20for%20them%20to%20speak%20about%20Emergency%20and%20being%20a%20democrat%2C%20I%20mean%20what%20can%20I%20say%3F%20Comedy!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F02135219%2Fmodi-bhagwat.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F02135219%2Fmodi-bhagwat.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F02135219%2Fmodi-bhagwat-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F02135219%2Fmodi-bhagwat-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-452366%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20photo%20of%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20and%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3