0the%20pulp%20of%20fruits%2C%20we%20stuff%20%3Cem%3Ekesar%20pista%20kulfi%3C%2Fem%3E%20inside%20the%20peel.%20We%20then%20seal%20that%20fruit%20using%20wheat%20dough%20and%20store%20it%20inside%20a%20%3Cem%3Ematka%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20three%20to%20four%20hours.%20The%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3Es%20are%20sliced%20and%20then%20served%20to%20customers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20love%20our%20stuffed%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20While%20local%20people%20order%20these%20for%20guests%2C%20we%20get%20many%20domestic%20and%20international%20tourists%20who%20enjoy%20them.%20These%20are%20very%20unique%20and%20one-of-a-kind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharad%20Gupta%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%20at%20the%20Kuremal%E2%80%99s%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20visit%20the%20place%20once%20every%20two%20weeks%2C%20and%20when%20my%20friends%20from%20the%20US%20visit%2C%20we%20always%20take%20them%20to%20this%20eatery.%20It%E2%80%99s%20our%20must-go%20place%20for%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Once%2C%20seven%20of%20our%20friends%20went%20there%20and%20exhausted%20all%20of%20their%20tamarind-flavoured%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20Even%20my%20children%20love%20it%20here.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20better%20taste%20in%20any%20other%20ice%20cream%20brands.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F254840%2Fishan-soni-roshan-lal-soni-roshan-di-kulfi-iconic-eatery-delhi-sweets-partition-of-india-karol-bagh-1997-bomb-blasts-family-legacy-food-business-culture-div200%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eiconic%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%2055%20flavours%20and%20manufactures%20about%206%2C000%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3Es%20in%20a%20day.%20For%20Vishal%2C%20it%20is%20extremely%20satisfying%20to%20keep%20the%20legacy%20alive.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20glad%20I%20quit%20my%20desk%20job%20and%20joined%20my%20fami